465 { ngx_string("X-Accel-Charset"), NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_XA_CHARSET },
466 { ngx_string("Expires"), NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_EXPIRES },
467 { ngx_string("Cache-Control"), NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_CACHE_CONTROL },
468 { ngx_string("Set-Cookie"), NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_SET_COOKIE },
469 { ngx_string("Vary"), NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_VARY },
470 { ngx_null_string, 0 }
471};
472
473
474ngx_int_t
475ngx_http_upstream_create(ngx_http_request_t *r)
476{
477 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
478
479 u = r->upstream;
480
481 if (u && u->cleanup) {
482 r->main->count++;
483 ngx_http_upstream_cleanup(r);
484 }
485
486 u = ngx_pcalloc(r->pool, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_t));
487 if (u == NULL) {
488 return NGX_ERROR;
489 }
490
491 r->upstream = u;
492
493 u->peer.log = r->connection->log;
494 u->peer.log_error = NGX_ERROR_ERR;
495
496#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
497 r->cache = NULL;
498#endif
499
500 u->headers_in.content_length_n = -1;
501 u->headers_in.last_modified_time = -1;
502
503 return NGX_OK;
504}
505
506
507void
508ngx_http_upstream_init(ngx_http_request_t *r)
509{
510 ngx_connection_t *c;
511
512 c = r->connection;
513
514 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
515 "http init upstream, client timer: %d", c->read->timer_set);
516
517#if (NGX_HTTP_V2)
518 if (r->stream) {
519 ngx_http_upstream_init_request(r);
520 return;
521 }
522#endif
523
524 if (c->read->timer_set) {
525 ngx_del_timer(c->read);
526 }
527
528 if (ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_CLEAR_EVENT) {
529
530 if (!c->write->active) {
531 if (ngx_add_event(c->write, NGX_WRITE_EVENT, NGX_CLEAR_EVENT)
532 == NGX_ERROR)
533 {
534 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
535 return;
536 }
537 }
538 }
539
540 ngx_http_upstream_init_request(r);
541}
542
543
544static void
545ngx_http_upstream_init_request(ngx_http_request_t *r)
546{
547 ngx_str_t *host;
548 ngx_uint_t i;
549 ngx_resolver_ctx_t *ctx, temp;
550 ngx_http_cleanup_t *cln;
551 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
552 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
553 ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t *uscf, **uscfp;
554 ngx_http_upstream_main_conf_t *umcf;
555
556 if (r->aio) {
557 return;
558 }
559
560 u = r->upstream;
561
562#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
563
564 if (u->conf->cache) {
565 ngx_int_t rc;
566
567 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache(r, u);
568
569 if (rc == NGX_BUSY) {
570 r->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_init_request;
571 return;
572 }
573
574 r->write_event_handler = ngx_http_request_empty_handler;
575
576 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
577 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
578 return;
579 }
580
581 if (rc == NGX_OK) {
582 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache_send(r, u);
583
584 if (rc == NGX_DONE) {
585 return;
586 }
587
588 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER) {
589 rc = NGX_DECLINED;
590 r->cached = 0;
591 u->buffer.start = NULL;
592 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_MISS;
593 u->request_sent = 1;
594 }
595
596 if (ngx_http_upstream_cache_background_update(r, u) != NGX_OK) {
597 rc = NGX_ERROR;
598 }
599 }
600
601 if (rc != NGX_DECLINED) {
602 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, rc);
603 return;
604 }
605 }
606
607#endif
608
609 u->store = u->conf->store;
610
611 if (!u->store && !r->post_action && !u->conf->ignore_client_abort) {
612 r->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_rd_check_broken_connection;
613 r->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_wr_check_broken_connection;
614 }
615
616 if (r->request_body) {
617 u->request_bufs = r->request_body->bufs;
618 }
619
620 if (u->create_request(r) != NGX_OK) {
621 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
622 return;
623 }
624
625 if (ngx_http_upstream_set_local(r, u, u->conf->local) != NGX_OK) {
626 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
627 return;
628 }
629
630 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
631
632 u->output.alignment = clcf->directio_alignment;
633 u->output.pool = r->pool;
634 u->output.bufs.num = 1;
635 u->output.bufs.size = clcf->client_body_buffer_size;
636
637 if (u->output.output_filter == NULL) {
638 u->output.output_filter = ngx_chain_writer;
639 u->output.filter_ctx = &u->writer;
640 }
641
642 u->writer.pool = r->pool;
643
644 if (r->upstream_states == NULL) {
645
646 r->upstream_states = ngx_array_create(r->pool, 1,
647 sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_state_t));
648 if (r->upstream_states == NULL) {
649 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
650 return;
651 }
652
653 } else {
654
655 u->state = ngx_array_push(r->upstream_states);
656 if (u->state == NULL) {
657 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
658 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
659 return;
660 }
661
662 ngx_memzero(u->state, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_state_t));
663 }
664
665 cln = ngx_http_cleanup_add(r, 0);
666 if (cln == NULL) {
667 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
668 return;
669 }
670
671 cln->handler = ngx_http_upstream_cleanup;
672 cln->data = r;
673 u->cleanup = &cln->handler;
674
675 if (u->resolved == NULL) {
676
677 uscf = u->conf->upstream;
678
679 } else {
680
681#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
682 u->ssl_name = u->resolved->host;
683#endif
684
685 host = &u->resolved->host;
686
687 umcf = ngx_http_get_module_main_conf(r, ngx_http_upstream_module);
688
689 uscfp = umcf->upstreams.elts;
690
691 for (i = 0; i < umcf->upstreams.nelts; i++) {
692
693 uscf = uscfp[i];
694
695 if (uscf->host.len == host->len
696 && ((uscf->port == 0 && u->resolved->no_port)
697 || uscf->port == u->resolved->port)
698 && ngx_strncasecmp(uscf->host.data, host->data, host->len) == 0)
699 {
700 goto found;
701 }
702 }
703
704 if (u->resolved->sockaddr) {
705
706 if (u->resolved->port == 0
707 && u->resolved->sockaddr->sa_family != AF_UNIX)
708 {
709 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
710 "no port in upstream \"%V\"", host);
711 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
712 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
713 return;
714 }
715
716 if (ngx_http_upstream_create_round_robin_peer(r, u->resolved)
717 != NGX_OK)
718 {
719 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
720 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
721 return;
722 }
723
724 ngx_http_upstream_connect(r, u);
725
726 return;
727 }
728
729 if (u->resolved->port == 0) {
730 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
731 "no port in upstream \"%V\"", host);
732 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
733 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
734 return;
735 }
736
737 temp.name = *host;
738
739 ctx = ngx_resolve_start(clcf->resolver, &temp);
740 if (ctx == NULL) {
741 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
742 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
743 return;
744 }
745
746 if (ctx == NGX_NO_RESOLVER) {
747 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
748 "no resolver defined to resolve %V", host);
749
750 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY);
751 return;
752 }
753
754 ctx->name = *host;
755 ctx->handler = ngx_http_upstream_resolve_handler;
756 ctx->data = r;
757 ctx->timeout = clcf->resolver_timeout;
758
759 u->resolved->ctx = ctx;
760
761 if (ngx_resolve_name(ctx) != NGX_OK) {
762 u->resolved->ctx = NULL;
763 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
764 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
765 return;
766 }
767
768 return;
769 }
770
771found:
772
773 if (uscf == NULL) {
774 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ALERT, r->connection->log, 0,
775 "no upstream configuration");
776 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
777 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
778 return;
779 }
780
781 u->upstream = uscf;
782
783#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
784 u->ssl_name = uscf->host;
785#endif
786
787 if (uscf->peer.init(r, uscf) != NGX_OK) {
788 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
789 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
790 return;
791 }
792
793 u->peer.start_time = ngx_current_msec;
794
795 if (u->conf->next_upstream_tries
796 && u->peer.tries > u->conf->next_upstream_tries)
797 {
798 u->peer.tries = u->conf->next_upstream_tries;
799 }
800
801 ngx_http_upstream_connect(r, u);
802}
803
804
805#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
806
807static ngx_int_t
808ngx_http_upstream_cache(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
809{
810 ngx_int_t rc;
811 ngx_http_cache_t *c;
812 ngx_http_file_cache_t *cache;
813
814 c = r->cache;
815
816 if (c == NULL) {
817
818 if (!(r->method & u->conf->cache_methods)) {
819 return NGX_DECLINED;
820 }
821
822 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache_get(r, u, &cache);
823
824 if (rc != NGX_OK) {
825 return rc;
826 }
827
828 if (r->method == NGX_HTTP_HEAD && u->conf->cache_convert_head) {
829 u->method = ngx_http_core_get_method;
830 }
831
832 if (ngx_http_file_cache_new(r) != NGX_OK) {
833 return NGX_ERROR;
834 }
835
836 if (u->create_key(r) != NGX_OK) {
837 return NGX_ERROR;
838 }
839
840 /* TODO: add keys */
841
842 ngx_http_file_cache_create_key(r);
843
844 if (r->cache->header_start + 256 >= u->conf->buffer_size) {
845 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
846 "%V_buffer_size %uz is not enough for cache key, "
847 "it should be increased to at least %uz",
848 &u->conf->module, u->conf->buffer_size,
849 ngx_align(r->cache->header_start + 256, 1024));
850
851 r->cache = NULL;
852 return NGX_DECLINED;
853 }
854
855 u->cacheable = 1;
856
857 c = r->cache;
858
859 c->body_start = u->conf->buffer_size;
860 c->min_uses = u->conf->cache_min_uses;
861 c->file_cache = cache;
862
863 switch (ngx_http_test_predicates(r, u->conf->cache_bypass)) {
864
865 case NGX_ERROR:
866 return NGX_ERROR;
867
868 case NGX_DECLINED:
869 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_BYPASS;
870 return NGX_DECLINED;
871
872 default: /* NGX_OK */
873 break;
874 }
875
876 c->lock = u->conf->cache_lock;
877 c->lock_timeout = u->conf->cache_lock_timeout;
878 c->lock_age = u->conf->cache_lock_age;
879
880 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_MISS;
881 }
882
883 rc = ngx_http_file_cache_open(r);
884
885 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
886 "http upstream cache: %i", rc);
887
888 switch (rc) {
889
890 case NGX_HTTP_CACHE_STALE:
891
892 if (((u->conf->cache_use_stale & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_UPDATING)
893 || c->stale_updating) && !r->background
894 && u->conf->cache_background_update)
895 {
896 r->cache->background = 1;
897 u->cache_status = rc;
898 rc = NGX_OK;
899 }
900
901 break;
902
903 case NGX_HTTP_CACHE_UPDATING:
904
905 if (((u->conf->cache_use_stale & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_UPDATING)
906 || c->stale_updating) && !r->background)
907 {
908 u->cache_status = rc;
909 rc = NGX_OK;
910
911 } else {
912 rc = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_STALE;
913 }
914
915 break;
916
917 case NGX_OK:
918 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_HIT;
919 }
920
921 switch (rc) {
922
923 case NGX_OK:
924
925 return NGX_OK;
926
927 case NGX_HTTP_CACHE_STALE:
928
929 c->valid_sec = 0;
930 c->updating_sec = 0;
931 c->error_sec = 0;
932
933 u->buffer.start = NULL;
934 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_EXPIRED;
935
936 break;
937
938 case NGX_DECLINED:
939
940 if ((size_t) (u->buffer.end - u->buffer.start) < u->conf->buffer_size) {
941 u->buffer.start = NULL;
942
943 } else {
944 u->buffer.pos = u->buffer.start + c->header_start;
945 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.pos;
946 }
947
948 break;
949
950 case NGX_HTTP_CACHE_SCARCE:
951
952 u->cacheable = 0;
953
954 break;
955
956 case NGX_AGAIN:
957
958 return NGX_BUSY;
959
960 case NGX_ERROR:
961
962 return NGX_ERROR;
963
964 default:
965
966 /* cached NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY, NGX_HTTP_GATEWAY_TIME_OUT, etc. */
967
968 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_HIT;
969
970 return rc;
971 }
972
973 if (ngx_http_upstream_cache_check_range(r, u) == NGX_DECLINED) {
974 u->cacheable = 0;
975 }
976
977 r->cached = 0;
978
979 return NGX_DECLINED;
980}
981
982
983static ngx_int_t
984ngx_http_upstream_cache_get(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
985 ngx_http_file_cache_t **cache)
986{
987 ngx_str_t *name, val;
988 ngx_uint_t i;
989 ngx_http_file_cache_t **caches;
990
991 if (u->conf->cache_zone) {
992 *cache = u->conf->cache_zone->data;
993 return NGX_OK;
994 }
995
996 if (ngx_http_complex_value(r, u->conf->cache_value, &val) != NGX_OK) {
997 return NGX_ERROR;
998 }
999
1000 if (val.len == 0
1001 || (val.len == 3 && ngx_strncmp(val.data, "off", 3) == 0))
1002 {
1003 return NGX_DECLINED;
1004 }
1005
1006 caches = u->caches->elts;
1007
1008 for (i = 0; i < u->caches->nelts; i++) {
1009 name = &caches[i]->shm_zone->shm.name;
1010
1011 if (name->len == val.len
1012 && ngx_strncmp(name->data, val.data, val.len) == 0)
1013 {
1014 *cache = caches[i];
1015 return NGX_OK;
1016 }
1017 }
1018
1019 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
1020 "cache \"%V\" not found", &val);
1021
1022 return NGX_ERROR;
1023}
1024
1025
1026static ngx_int_t
1027ngx_http_upstream_cache_send(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
1028{
1029 ngx_int_t rc;
1030 ngx_http_cache_t *c;
1031
1032 r->cached = 1;
1033 c = r->cache;
1034
1035 if (c->header_start == c->body_start) {
1036 r->http_version = NGX_HTTP_VERSION_9;
1037 return ngx_http_cache_send(r);
1038 }
1039
1040 /* TODO: cache stack */
1041
1042 u->buffer = *c->buf;
1043 u->buffer.pos += c->header_start;
1044
1045 ngx_memzero(&u->headers_in, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_headers_in_t));
1046 u->headers_in.content_length_n = -1;
1047 u->headers_in.last_modified_time = -1;
1048
1049 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.headers, r->pool, 8,
1050 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
1051 != NGX_OK)
1052 {
1053 return NGX_ERROR;
1054 }
1055
1056 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.trailers, r->pool, 2,
1057 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
1058 != NGX_OK)
1059 {
1060 return NGX_ERROR;
1061 }
1062
1063 rc = u->process_header(r);
1064
1065 if (rc == NGX_OK) {
1066
1067 if (ngx_http_upstream_process_headers(r, u) != NGX_OK) {
1068 return NGX_DONE;
1069 }
1070
1071 return ngx_http_cache_send(r);
1072 }
1073
1074 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
1075 return NGX_ERROR;
1076 }
1077
1078 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
1079 rc = NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER;
1080 }
1081
1082 /* rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER */
1083
1084 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_CRIT, r->connection->log, 0,
1085 "cache file \"%s\" contains invalid header",
1086 c->file.name.data);
1087
1088 /* TODO: delete file */
1089
1090 return rc;
1091}

1093
1094static ngx_int_t
1095ngx_http_upstream_cache_background_update(ngx_http_request_t *r,
1096 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
1097{
1098 ngx_http_request_t *sr;
1099
1100 if (!r->cached || !r->cache->background) {
1101 return NGX_OK;
1102 }
1103
1104 if (r == r->main) {
1105 r->preserve_body = 1;
1106 }
1107
1108 if (ngx_http_subrequest(r, &r->uri, &r->args, &sr, NULL,
1109 NGX_HTTP_SUBREQUEST_CLONE
1110 |NGX_HTTP_SUBREQUEST_BACKGROUND)
1111 != NGX_OK)
1112 {
1113 return NGX_ERROR;
1114 }
1115
1116 sr->header_only = 1;
1117
1118 return NGX_OK;
1119}
1120
1121
1122static ngx_int_t
1123ngx_http_upstream_cache_check_range(ngx_http_request_t *r,
1124 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
1125{
1126 off_t offset;
1127 u_char *p, *start;
1128 ngx_table_elt_t *h;
1129
1130 h = r->headers_in.range;
1131
1132 if (h == NULL
1133 || !u->cacheable
1134 || u->conf->cache_max_range_offset == NGX_MAX_OFF_T_VALUE)
1135 {
1136 return NGX_OK;
1137 }
1138
1139 if (u->conf->cache_max_range_offset == 0) {
1140 return NGX_DECLINED;
1141 }
1142
1143 if (h->value.len < 7
1144 || ngx_strncasecmp(h->value.data, (u_char *) "bytes=", 6) != 0)
1145 {
1146 return NGX_OK;
1147 }
1148
1149 p = h->value.data + 6;
1150
1151 while (*p == ' ') { p++; }
1152
1153 if (*p == '-') {
1154 return NGX_DECLINED;
1155 }
1156
1157 start = p;
1158
1159 while (*p >= '0' && *p <= '9') { p++; }
1160
1161 offset = ngx_atoof(start, p - start);
1162
1163 if (offset >= u->conf->cache_max_range_offset) {
1164 return NGX_DECLINED;
1165 }
1166
1167 return NGX_OK;
1168}

1170#endif

1172
1173static void
1174ngx_http_upstream_resolve_handler(ngx_resolver_ctx_t *ctx)
1175{
1176 ngx_uint_t run_posted;
1177 ngx_connection_t *c;
1178 ngx_http_request_t *r;
1179 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
1180 ngx_http_upstream_resolved_t *ur;
1181
1182 run_posted = ctx->async;
1183
1184 r = ctx->data;
1185 c = r->connection;
1186
1187 u = r->upstream;
1188 ur = u->resolved;
1189
1190 ngx_http_set_log_request(c->log, r);
1191
1192 ngx_log_debug2(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
1193 "http upstream resolve: \"%V?%V\"", &r->uri, &r->args);
1194
1195 if (ctx->state) {
1196 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
1197 "%V could not be resolved (%i: %s)",
1198 &ctx->name, ctx->state,
1199 ngx_resolver_strerror(ctx->state));
1200
1201 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY);
1202 goto failed;
1203 }
1204
1205 ur->naddrs = ctx->naddrs;
1206 ur->addrs = ctx->addrs;
1207
1208#if (NGX_DEBUG)
1209 {
1210 u_char text[NGX_SOCKADDR_STRLEN];
1211 ngx_str_t addr;
1212 ngx_uint_t i;
1213
1214 addr.data = text;
1215
1216 for (i = 0; i < ctx->naddrs; i++) {
1217 addr.len = ngx_sock_ntop(ur->addrs[i].sockaddr, ur->addrs[i].socklen,
1218 text, NGX_SOCKADDR_STRLEN, 0);
1219
1220 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
1221 "name was resolved to %V", &addr);
1222 }
1223 }
1224#endif
1225
1226 if (ngx_http_upstream_create_round_robin_peer(r, ur) != NGX_OK) {
1227 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1228 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1229 goto failed;
1230 }
1231
1232 ngx_resolve_name_done(ctx);
1233 ur->ctx = NULL;
1234
1235 u->peer.start_time = ngx_current_msec;
1236
1237 if (u->conf->next_upstream_tries
1238 && u->peer.tries > u->conf->next_upstream_tries)
1239 {
1240 u->peer.tries = u->conf->next_upstream_tries;
1241 }
1242
1243 ngx_http_upstream_connect(r, u);
1244
1245failed:
1246
1247 if (run_posted) {
1248 ngx_http_run_posted_requests(c);
1249 }
1250}
1251
1252
1253static void
1254ngx_http_upstream_handler(ngx_event_t *ev)
1255{
1256 ngx_connection_t *c;
1257 ngx_http_request_t *r;
1258 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
1259
1260 c = ev->data;
1261 r = c->data;
1262
1263 u = r->upstream;
1264 c = r->connection;
1265
1266 ngx_http_set_log_request(c->log, r);
1267
1268 ngx_log_debug2(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
1269 "http upstream request: \"%V?%V\"", &r->uri, &r->args);
1270
1271 if (ev->delayed && ev->timedout) {
1272 ev->delayed = 0;
1273 ev->timedout = 0;
1274 }
1275
1276 if (ev->write) {
1277 u->write_event_handler(r, u);
1278
1279 } else {
1280 u->read_event_handler(r, u);
1281 }
1282
1283 ngx_http_run_posted_requests(c);
1284}

1300
1301static void
1302ngx_http_upstream_check_broken_connection(ngx_http_request_t *r,
1303 ngx_event_t *ev)
1304{
1305 int n;
1306 char buf[1];
1307 ngx_err_t err;
1308 ngx_int_t event;
1309 ngx_connection_t *c;
1310 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
1311
1312 ngx_log_debug2(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, ev->log, 0,
1313 "http upstream check client, write event:%d, \"%V\"",
1314 ev->write, &r->uri);
1315
1316 c = r->connection;
1317 u = r->upstream;
1318
1319 if (c->error) {
1320 if ((ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_LEVEL_EVENT) && ev->active) {
1321
1322 event = ev->write ? NGX_WRITE_EVENT : NGX_READ_EVENT;
1323
1324 if (ngx_del_event(ev, event, 0) != NGX_OK) {
1325 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1326 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1327 return;
1328 }
1329 }
1330
1331 if (!u->cacheable) {
1332 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1333 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1334 }
1335
1336 return;
1337 }
1338
1339#if (NGX_HTTP_V2)
1340 if (r->stream) {
1341 return;
1342 }
1343#endif
1344
1345#if (NGX_HAVE_KQUEUE)
1346
1347 if (ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_KQUEUE_EVENT) {
1348
1349 if (!ev->pending_eof) {
1350 return;
1351 }
1352
1353 ev->eof = 1;
1354 c->error = 1;
1355
1356 if (ev->kq_errno) {
1357 ev->error = 1;
1358 }
1359
1360 if (!u->cacheable && u->peer.connection) {
1361 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, ev->kq_errno,
1362 "kevent() reported that client prematurely closed "
1363 "connection, so upstream connection is closed too");
1364 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1365 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1366 return;
1367 }
1368
1369 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, ev->kq_errno,
1370 "kevent() reported that client prematurely closed "
1371 "connection");
1372
1373 if (u->peer.connection == NULL) {
1374 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1375 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1376 }
1377
1378 return;
1379 }
1380
1381#endif
1382
1383#if (NGX_HAVE_EPOLLRDHUP)
1384
1385 if ((ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_EPOLL_EVENT) && ngx_use_epoll_rdhup) {
1386 socklen_t len;
1387
1388 if (!ev->pending_eof) {
1389 return;
1390 }
1391
1392 ev->eof = 1;
1393 c->error = 1;
1394
1395 err = 0;
1396 len = sizeof(ngx_err_t);
1397
1398 /*
1399 * BSDs and Linux return 0 and set a pending error in err
1400 * Solaris returns -1 and sets errno
1401 */
1402
1403 if (getsockopt(c->fd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_ERROR, (void *) &err, &len)
1404 == -1)
1405 {
1406 err = ngx_socket_errno;
1407 }
1408
1409 if (err) {
1410 ev->error = 1;
1411 }
1412
1413 if (!u->cacheable && u->peer.connection) {
1414 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, err,
1415 "epoll_wait() reported that client prematurely closed "
1416 "connection, so upstream connection is closed too");
1417 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1418 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1419 return;
1420 }
1421
1422 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, err,
1423 "epoll_wait() reported that client prematurely closed "
1424 "connection");
1425
1426 if (u->peer.connection == NULL) {
1427 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1428 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1429 }
1430
1431 return;
1432 }
1433
1434#endif
1435
1436 n = recv(c->fd, buf, 1, MSG_PEEK);
1437
1438 err = ngx_socket_errno;
1439
1440 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, ev->log, err,
1441 "http upstream recv(): %d", n);
1442
1443 if (ev->write && (n >= 0 || err == NGX_EAGAIN)) {
1444 return;
1445 }
1446
1447 if ((ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_LEVEL_EVENT) && ev->active) {
1448
1449 event = ev->write ? NGX_WRITE_EVENT : NGX_READ_EVENT;
1450
1451 if (ngx_del_event(ev, event, 0) != NGX_OK) {
1452 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1453 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1454 return;
1455 }
1456 }
1457
1458 if (n > 0) {
1459 return;
1460 }
1461
1462 if (n == -1) {
1463 if (err == NGX_EAGAIN) {
1464 return;
1465 }
1466
1467 ev->error = 1;
1468
1469 } else { /* n == 0 */
1470 err = 0;
1471 }
1472
1473 ev->eof = 1;
1474 c->error = 1;
1475
1476 if (!u->cacheable && u->peer.connection) {
1477 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, err,
1478 "client prematurely closed connection, "
1479 "so upstream connection is closed too");
1480 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1481 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1482 return;
1483 }
1484
1485 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_INFO, ev->log, err,
1486 "client prematurely closed connection");
1487
1488 if (u->peer.connection == NULL) {
1489 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1490 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
1491 }
1492}
1493
1494
1495static void
1496ngx_http_upstream_connect(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
1497{
1498 ngx_int_t rc;
1499 ngx_connection_t *c;
1500
1501 r->connection->log->action = "connecting to upstream";
1502
1503 if (u->state && u->state->response_time) {
1504 u->state->response_time = ngx_current_msec - u->state->response_time;
1505 }
1506
1507 u->state = ngx_array_push(r->upstream_states);
1508 if (u->state == NULL) {
1509 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1510 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1511 return;
1512 }
1513
1514 ngx_memzero(u->state, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_state_t));
1515
1516 u->state->response_time = ngx_current_msec;
1517 u->state->connect_time = (ngx_msec_t) -1;
1518 u->state->header_time = (ngx_msec_t) -1;
1519
1520 rc = ngx_event_connect_peer(&u->peer);
1521
1522 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
1523 "http upstream connect: %i", rc);
1524
1525 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
1526 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1527 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1528 return;
1529 }
1530
1531 u->state->peer = u->peer.name;
1532
1533 if (rc == NGX_BUSY) {
1534 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0, "no live upstreams");
1535 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_NOLIVE);
1536 return;
1537 }
1538
1539 if (rc == NGX_DECLINED) {
1540 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
1541 return;
1542 }
1543
1544 /* rc == NGX_OK || rc == NGX_AGAIN || rc == NGX_DONE */
1545
1546 c = u->peer.connection;
1547
1548 c->data = r;
1549
1550 c->write->handler = ngx_http_upstream_handler;
1551 c->read->handler = ngx_http_upstream_handler;
1552
1553 u->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_send_request_handler;
1554 u->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_process_header;
1555
1556 c->sendfile &= r->connection->sendfile;
1557 u->output.sendfile = c->sendfile;
1558
1559 if (c->pool == NULL) {
1560
1561 /* we need separate pool here to be able to cache SSL connections */
1562
1563 c->pool = ngx_create_pool(128, r->connection->log);
1564 if (c->pool == NULL) {
1565 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1566 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1567 return;
1568 }
1569 }
1570
1571 c->log = r->connection->log;
1572 c->pool->log = c->log;
1573 c->read->log = c->log;
1574 c->write->log = c->log;
1575
1576 /* init or reinit the ngx_output_chain() and ngx_chain_writer() contexts */
1577
1578 u->writer.out = NULL;
1579 u->writer.last = &u->writer.out;
1580 u->writer.connection = c;
1581 u->writer.limit = 0;
1582
1583 if (u->request_sent) {
1584 if (ngx_http_upstream_reinit(r, u) != NGX_OK) {
1585 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1586 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1587 return;
1588 }
1589 }
1590
1591 if (r->request_body
1592 && r->request_body->buf
1593 && r->request_body->temp_file
1594 && r == r->main)
1595 {
1596 /*
1597 * the r->request_body->buf can be reused for one request only,
1598 * the subrequests should allocate their own temporary bufs
1599 */
1600
1601 u->output.free = ngx_alloc_chain_link(r->pool);
1602 if (u->output.free == NULL) {
1603 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1604 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1605 return;
1606 }
1607
1608 u->output.free->buf = r->request_body->buf;
1609 u->output.free->next = NULL;
1610 u->output.allocated = 1;
1611
1612 r->request_body->buf->pos = r->request_body->buf->start;
1613 r->request_body->buf->last = r->request_body->buf->start;
1614 r->request_body->buf->tag = u->output.tag;
1615 }
1616
1617 u->request_sent = 0;
1618 u->request_body_sent = 0;
1619 u->request_body_blocked = 0;
1620
1621 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
1622 ngx_add_timer(c->write, u->conf->connect_timeout);
1623 return;
1624 }
1625
1626#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
1627
1628 if (u->ssl && c->ssl == NULL) {
1629 ngx_http_upstream_ssl_init_connection(r, u, c);
1630 return;
1631 }
1632
1633#endif
1634
1635 ngx_http_upstream_send_request(r, u, 1);
1636}
1637
1638
1639#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
1640
1641static void
1642ngx_http_upstream_ssl_init_connection(ngx_http_request_t *r,
1643 ngx_http_upstream_t *u, ngx_connection_t *c)
1644{
1645 ngx_int_t rc;
1646 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
1647
1648 if (ngx_http_upstream_test_connect(c) != NGX_OK) {
1649 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
1650 return;
1651 }
1652
1653 if (ngx_ssl_create_connection(u->conf->ssl, c,
1654 NGX_SSL_BUFFER|NGX_SSL_CLIENT)
1655 != NGX_OK)
1656 {
1657 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1658 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1659 return;
1660 }
1661
1662 c->sendfile = 0;
1663 u->output.sendfile = 0;
1664
1665 if (u->conf->ssl_server_name || u->conf->ssl_verify) {
1666 if (ngx_http_upstream_ssl_name(r, u, c) != NGX_OK) {
1667 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1668 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1669 return;
1670 }
1671 }
1672
1673 if (u->conf->ssl_session_reuse) {
1674 if (u->peer.set_session(&u->peer, u->peer.data) != NGX_OK) {
1675 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1676 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1677 return;
1678 }
1679
1680 /* abbreviated SSL handshake may interact badly with Nagle */
1681
1682 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
1683
1684 if (clcf->tcp_nodelay && ngx_tcp_nodelay(c) != NGX_OK) {
1685 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
1686 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
1687 return;
1688 }
1689 }
1690
1691 r->connection->log->action = "SSL handshaking to upstream";
1692
1693 rc = ngx_ssl_handshake(c);
1694
1695 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
1696
1697 if (!c->write->timer_set) {
1698 ngx_add_timer(c->write, u->conf->connect_timeout);
1699 }
1700
1701 c->ssl->handler = ngx_http_upstream_ssl_handshake_handler;
1702 return;
1703 }
1704
1705 ngx_http_upstream_ssl_handshake(r, u, c);
1706}
1707
1708
1709static void
1710ngx_http_upstream_ssl_handshake_handler(ngx_connection_t *c)
1711{
1712 ngx_http_request_t *r;
1713 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
1714
1715 r = c->data;
1716
1717 u = r->upstream;
1718 c = r->connection;
1719
1720 ngx_http_set_log_request(c->log, r);
1721
1722 ngx_log_debug2(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
1723 "http upstream ssl handshake: \"%V?%V\"",
1724 &r->uri, &r->args);
1725
1726 ngx_http_upstream_ssl_handshake(r, u, u->peer.connection);
1727
1728 ngx_http_run_posted_requests(c);
1729}

1731
1732static void
1733ngx_http_upstream_ssl_handshake(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
1734 ngx_connection_t *c)
1735{
1736 long rc;
1737
1738 if (c->ssl->handshaked) {
1739
1740 if (u->conf->ssl_verify) {
1741 rc = SSL_get_verify_result(c->ssl->connection);
1742
1743 if (rc != X509_V_OK) {
1744 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, c->log, 0,
1745 "upstream SSL certificate verify error: (%l:%s)",
1746 rc, X509_verify_cert_error_string(rc));
1747 goto failed;
1748 }
1749
1750 if (ngx_ssl_check_host(c, &u->ssl_name) != NGX_OK) {
1751 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, c->log, 0,
1752 "upstream SSL certificate does not match \"%V\"",
1753 &u->ssl_name);
1754 goto failed;
1755 }
1756 }
1757
1758 if (u->conf->ssl_session_reuse) {
1759 u->peer.save_session(&u->peer, u->peer.data);
1760 }
1761
1762 c->write->handler = ngx_http_upstream_handler;
1763 c->read->handler = ngx_http_upstream_handler;
1764
1765 ngx_http_upstream_send_request(r, u, 1);
1766
1767 return;
1768 }
1769
1770 if (c->write->timedout) {
1771 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_TIMEOUT);
1772 return;
1773 }
1774
1775failed:
1776
1777 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
1778}
1779
1780
1781static ngx_int_t
1782ngx_http_upstream_ssl_name(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
1783 ngx_connection_t *c)
1784{
1785 u_char *p, *last;
1786 ngx_str_t name;
1787
1788 if (u->conf->ssl_name) {
1789 if (ngx_http_complex_value(r, u->conf->ssl_name, &name) != NGX_OK) {
1790 return NGX_ERROR;
1791 }
1792
1793 } else {
1794 name = u->ssl_name;
1795 }
1796
1797 if (name.len == 0) {
1798 goto done;
1799 }
1800
1801 /*
1802 * ssl name here may contain port, notably if derived from $proxy_host
1803 * or $http_host; we have to strip it
1804 */
1805
1806 p = name.data;
1807 last = name.data + name.len;
1808
1809 if (*p == '[') {
1810 p = ngx_strlchr(p, last, ']');
1811
1812 if (p == NULL) {
1813 p = name.data;
1814 }
1815 }
1816
1817 p = ngx_strlchr(p, last, ':');
1818
1819 if (p != NULL) {
1820 name.len = p - name.data;
1821 }
1822
1823 if (!u->conf->ssl_server_name) {
1824 goto done;
1825 }
1826
1827#ifdef SSL_CTRL_SET_TLSEXT_HOSTNAME
1828
1829 /* as per RFC 6066, literal IPv4 and IPv6 addresses are not permitted */
1830
1831 if (name.len == 0 || *name.data == '[') {
1832 goto done;
1833 }
1834
1835 if (ngx_inet_addr(name.data, name.len) != INADDR_NONE) {
1836 goto done;
1837 }
1838
1839 /*
1840 * SSL_set_tlsext_host_name() needs a null-terminated string,
1841 * hence we explicitly null-terminate name here
1842 */
1843
1844 p = ngx_pnalloc(r->pool, name.len + 1);
1845 if (p == NULL) {
1846 return NGX_ERROR;
1847 }
1848
1849 (void) ngx_cpystrn(p, name.data, name.len + 1);
1850
1851 name.data = p;
1852
1853 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
1854 "upstream SSL server name: \"%s\"", name.data);
1855
1856 if (SSL_set_tlsext_host_name(c->ssl->connection,
1857 (char *) name.data)
1858 == 0)
1859 {
1860 ngx_ssl_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
1861 "SSL_set_tlsext_host_name(\"%s\") failed", name.data);
1862 return NGX_ERROR;
1863 }
1864
1865#endif
1866
1867done:
1868
1869 u->ssl_name = name;
1870
1871 return NGX_OK;
1872}
1873
1874#endif

1876
1877static ngx_int_t
1878ngx_http_upstream_reinit(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
1879{
1880 off_t file_pos;
1881 ngx_chain_t *cl;
1882
1883 if (u->reinit_request(r) != NGX_OK) {
1884 return NGX_ERROR;
1885 }
1886
1887 u->keepalive = 0;
1888 u->upgrade = 0;
1889
1890 ngx_memzero(&u->headers_in, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_headers_in_t));
1891 u->headers_in.content_length_n = -1;
1892 u->headers_in.last_modified_time = -1;
1893
1894 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.headers, r->pool, 8,
1895 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
1896 != NGX_OK)
1897 {
1898 return NGX_ERROR;
1899 }
1900
1901 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.trailers, r->pool, 2,
1902 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
1903 != NGX_OK)
1904 {
1905 return NGX_ERROR;
1906 }
1907
1908 /* reinit the request chain */
1909
1910 file_pos = 0;
1911
1912 for (cl = u->request_bufs; cl; cl = cl->next) {
1913 cl->buf->pos = cl->buf->start;
1914
1915 /* there is at most one file */
1916
1917 if (cl->buf->in_file) {
1918 cl->buf->file_pos = file_pos;
1919 file_pos = cl->buf->file_last;
1920 }
1921 }
1922
1923 /* reinit the subrequest's ngx_output_chain() context */
1924
1925 if (r->request_body && r->request_body->temp_file
1926 && r != r->main && u->output.buf)
1927 {
1928 u->output.free = ngx_alloc_chain_link(r->pool);
1929 if (u->output.free == NULL) {
1930 return NGX_ERROR;
1931 }
1932
1933 u->output.free->buf = u->output.buf;
1934 u->output.free->next = NULL;
1935
1936 u->output.buf->pos = u->output.buf->start;
1937 u->output.buf->last = u->output.buf->start;
1938 }
1939
1940 u->output.buf = NULL;
1941 u->output.in = NULL;
1942 u->output.busy = NULL;
1943
1944 /* reinit u->buffer */
1945
1946 u->buffer.pos = u->buffer.start;
1947
1948#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
1949
1950 if (r->cache) {
1951 u->buffer.pos += r->cache->header_start;
1952 }
1953
1954#endif
1955
1956 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.pos;
1957
1958 return NGX_OK;
1959}
1960
1961
1962static void
1963ngx_http_upstream_send_request(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
1964 ngx_uint_t do_write)
1965{
1966 ngx_int_t rc;
1967 ngx_connection_t *c;
1968
1969 c = u->peer.connection;
1970
1971 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
1972 "http upstream send request");
1973
1974 if (u->state->connect_time == (ngx_msec_t) -1) {
1975 u->state->connect_time = ngx_current_msec - u->state->response_time;
1976 }
1977
1978 if (!u->request_sent && ngx_http_upstream_test_connect(c) != NGX_OK) {
1979 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
1980 return;
1981 }
1982
1983 c->log->action = "sending request to upstream";
1984
1985 rc = ngx_http_upstream_send_request_body(r, u, do_write);
1986
1987 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
1988 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
1989 return;
1990 }
1991
1992 if (rc >= NGX_HTTP_SPECIAL_RESPONSE) {
1993 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
1994 return;
1995 }
1996
1997 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
1998 if (!c->write->ready || u->request_body_blocked) {
1999 ngx_add_timer(c->write, u->conf->send_timeout);
2000
2001 } else if (c->write->timer_set) {
2002 ngx_del_timer(c->write);
2003 }
2004
2005 if (ngx_handle_write_event(c->write, u->conf->send_lowat) != NGX_OK) {
2006 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2007 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2008 return;
2009 }
2010
2011 return;
2012 }
2013
2014 /* rc == NGX_OK */
2015
2016 u->request_body_sent = 1;
2017
2018 if (c->write->timer_set) {
2019 ngx_del_timer(c->write);
2020 }
2021
2022 if (c->tcp_nopush == NGX_TCP_NOPUSH_SET) {
2023 if (ngx_tcp_push(c->fd) == -1) {
2024 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_CRIT, c->log, ngx_socket_errno,
2025 ngx_tcp_push_n " failed");
2026 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2027 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2028 return;
2029 }
2030
2031 c->tcp_nopush = NGX_TCP_NOPUSH_UNSET;
2032 }
2033
2034 if (!u->conf->preserve_output) {
2035 u->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_dummy_handler;
2036 }
2037
2038 if (ngx_handle_write_event(c->write, 0) != NGX_OK) {
2039 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2040 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2041 return;
2042 }
2043
2044 ngx_add_timer(c->read, u->conf->read_timeout);
2045
2046 if (c->read->ready) {
2047 ngx_http_upstream_process_header(r, u);
2048 return;
2049 }
2050}

2052
2053static ngx_int_t
2054ngx_http_upstream_send_request_body(ngx_http_request_t *r,
2055 ngx_http_upstream_t *u, ngx_uint_t do_write)
2056{
2057 ngx_int_t rc;
2058 ngx_chain_t *out, *cl, *ln;
2059 ngx_connection_t *c;
2060 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
2061
2062 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
2063 "http upstream send request body");
2064
2065 if (!r->request_body_no_buffering) {
2066
2067 /* buffered request body */
2068
2069 if (!u->request_sent) {
2070 u->request_sent = 1;
2071 out = u->request_bufs;
2072
2073 } else {
2074 out = NULL;
2075 }
2076
2077 rc = ngx_output_chain(&u->output, out);
2078
2079 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
2080 u->request_body_blocked = 1;
2081
2082 } else {
2083 u->request_body_blocked = 0;
2084 }
2085
2086 return rc;
2087 }
2088
2089 if (!u->request_sent) {
2090 u->request_sent = 1;
2091 out = u->request_bufs;
2092
2093 if (r->request_body->bufs) {
2094 for (cl = out; cl->next; cl = out->next) { /* void */ }
2095 cl->next = r->request_body->bufs;
2096 r->request_body->bufs = NULL;
2097 }
2098
2099 c = u->peer.connection;
2100 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
2101
2102 if (clcf->tcp_nodelay && ngx_tcp_nodelay(c) != NGX_OK) {
2103 return NGX_ERROR;
2104 }
2105
2106 r->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_read_request_handler;
2107
2108 } else {
2109 out = NULL;
2110 }
2111
2112 for ( ;; ) {
2113
2114 if (do_write) {
2115 rc = ngx_output_chain(&u->output, out);
2116
2117 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
2118 return NGX_ERROR;
2119 }
2120
2121 while (out) {
2122 ln = out;
2123 out = out->next;
2124 ngx_free_chain(r->pool, ln);
2125 }
2126
2127 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
2128 u->request_body_blocked = 1;
2129
2130 } else {
2131 u->request_body_blocked = 0;
2132 }
2133
2134 if (rc == NGX_OK && !r->reading_body) {
2135 break;
2136 }
2137 }
2138
2139 if (r->reading_body) {
2140 /* read client request body */
2141
2142 rc = ngx_http_read_unbuffered_request_body(r);
2143
2144 if (rc >= NGX_HTTP_SPECIAL_RESPONSE) {
2145 return rc;
2146 }
2147
2148 out = r->request_body->bufs;
2149 r->request_body->bufs = NULL;
2150 }
2151
2152 /* stop if there is nothing to send */
2153
2154 if (out == NULL) {
2155 rc = NGX_AGAIN;
2156 break;
2157 }
2158
2159 do_write = 1;
2160 }
2161
2162 if (!r->reading_body) {
2163 if (!u->store && !r->post_action && !u->conf->ignore_client_abort) {
2164 r->read_event_handler =
2165 ngx_http_upstream_rd_check_broken_connection;
2166 }
2167 }
2168
2169 return rc;
2170}

2173static void
2174ngx_http_upstream_send_request_handler(ngx_http_request_t *r,
2175 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2176{
2177 ngx_connection_t *c;
2178
2179 c = u->peer.connection;
2180
2181 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
2182 "http upstream send request handler");
2183
2184 if (c->write->timedout) {
2185 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_TIMEOUT);
2186 return;
2187 }
2188
2189#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
2190
2191 if (u->ssl && c->ssl == NULL) {
2192 ngx_http_upstream_ssl_init_connection(r, u, c);
2193 return;
2194 }
2195
2196#endif
2197
2198 if (u->header_sent && !u->conf->preserve_output) {
2199 u->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_dummy_handler;
2200
2201 (void) ngx_handle_write_event(c->write, 0);
2202
2203 return;
2204 }
2205
2206 ngx_http_upstream_send_request(r, u, 1);
2207}

2231
2232static void
2233ngx_http_upstream_process_header(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2234{
2235 ssize_t n;
2236 ngx_int_t rc;
2237 ngx_connection_t *c;
2238
2239 c = u->peer.connection;
2240
2241 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
2242 "http upstream process header");
2243
2244 c->log->action = "reading response header from upstream";
2245
2246 if (c->read->timedout) {
2247 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_TIMEOUT);
2248 return;
2249 }
2250
2251 if (!u->request_sent && ngx_http_upstream_test_connect(c) != NGX_OK) {
2252 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
2253 return;
2254 }
2255
2256 if (u->buffer.start == NULL) {
2257 u->buffer.start = ngx_palloc(r->pool, u->conf->buffer_size);
2258 if (u->buffer.start == NULL) {
2259 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2260 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2261 return;
2262 }
2263
2264 u->buffer.pos = u->buffer.start;
2265 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.start;
2266 u->buffer.end = u->buffer.start + u->conf->buffer_size;
2267 u->buffer.temporary = 1;
2268
2269 u->buffer.tag = u->output.tag;
2270
2271 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.headers, r->pool, 8,
2272 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
2273 != NGX_OK)
2274 {
2275 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2276 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2277 return;
2278 }
2279
2280 if (ngx_list_init(&u->headers_in.trailers, r->pool, 2,
2281 sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t))
2282 != NGX_OK)
2283 {
2284 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2285 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2286 return;
2287 }
2288
2289#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2290
2291 if (r->cache) {
2292 u->buffer.pos += r->cache->header_start;
2293 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.pos;
2294 }
2295#endif
2296 }
2297
2298 for ( ;; ) {
2299
2300 n = c->recv(c, u->buffer.last, u->buffer.end - u->buffer.last);
2301
2302 if (n == NGX_AGAIN) {
2303#if 0
2304 ngx_add_timer(rev, u->read_timeout);
2305#endif
2306
2307 if (ngx_handle_read_event(c->read, 0) != NGX_OK) {
2308 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2309 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2310 return;
2311 }
2312
2313 return;
2314 }
2315
2316 if (n == 0) {
2317 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, c->log, 0,
2318 "upstream prematurely closed connection");
2319 }
2320
2321 if (n == NGX_ERROR || n == 0) {
2322 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR);
2323 return;
2324 }
2325
2326 u->state->bytes_received += n;
2327
2328 u->buffer.last += n;
2329
2330#if 0
2331 u->valid_header_in = 0;
2332
2333 u->peer.cached = 0;
2334#endif
2335
2336 rc = u->process_header(r);
2337
2338 if (rc == NGX_AGAIN) {
2339
2340 if (u->buffer.last == u->buffer.end) {
2341 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, c->log, 0,
2342 "upstream sent too big header");
2343
2344 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u,
2345 NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_INVALID_HEADER);
2346 return;
2347 }
2348
2349 continue;
2350 }
2351
2352 break;
2353 }
2354
2355 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER) {
2356 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_INVALID_HEADER);
2357 return;
2358 }
2359
2360 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
2361 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2362 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2363 return;
2364 }
2365
2366 /* rc == NGX_OK */
2367
2368 u->state->header_time = ngx_current_msec - u->state->response_time;
2369
2370 if (u->headers_in.status_n >= NGX_HTTP_SPECIAL_RESPONSE) {
2371
2372 if (ngx_http_upstream_test_next(r, u) == NGX_OK) {
2373 return;
2374 }
2375
2376 if (ngx_http_upstream_intercept_errors(r, u) == NGX_OK) {
2377 return;
2378 }
2379 }
2380
2381 if (ngx_http_upstream_process_headers(r, u) != NGX_OK) {
2382 return;
2383 }
2384
2385 ngx_http_upstream_send_response(r, u);
2386}

2388
2389static ngx_int_t
2390ngx_http_upstream_test_next(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2391{
2392 ngx_msec_t timeout;
2393 ngx_uint_t status, mask;
2394 ngx_http_upstream_next_t *un;
2395
2396 status = u->headers_in.status_n;
2397
2398 for (un = ngx_http_upstream_next_errors; un->status; un++) {
2399
2400 if (status != un->status) {
2401 continue;
2402 }
2403
2404 timeout = u->conf->next_upstream_timeout;
2405
2406 if (u->request_sent
2407 && (r->method & (NGX_HTTP_POST|NGX_HTTP_LOCK|NGX_HTTP_PATCH)))
2408 {
2409 mask = un->mask | NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_NON_IDEMPOTENT;
2410
2411 } else {
2412 mask = un->mask;
2413 }
2414
2415 if (u->peer.tries > 1
2416 && ((u->conf->next_upstream & mask) == mask)
2417 && !(u->request_sent && r->request_body_no_buffering)
2418 && !(timeout && ngx_current_msec - u->peer.start_time >= timeout))
2419 {
2420 ngx_http_upstream_next(r, u, un->mask);
2421 return NGX_OK;
2422 }
2423
2424#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2425
2426 if (u->cache_status == NGX_HTTP_CACHE_EXPIRED
2427 && ((u->conf->cache_use_stale & un->mask) || r->cache->stale_error))
2428 {
2429 ngx_int_t rc;
2430
2431 rc = u->reinit_request(r);
2432
2433 if (rc != NGX_OK) {
2434 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2435 return NGX_OK;
2436 }
2437
2438 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_STALE;
2439 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache_send(r, u);
2440
2441 if (rc == NGX_DONE) {
2442 return NGX_OK;
2443 }
2444
2445 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER) {
2446 rc = NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR;
2447 }
2448
2449 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2450 return NGX_OK;
2451 }
2452
2453#endif
2454 }
2455
2456#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2457
2458 if (status == NGX_HTTP_NOT_MODIFIED
2459 && u->cache_status == NGX_HTTP_CACHE_EXPIRED
2460 && u->conf->cache_revalidate)
2461 {
2462 time_t now, valid, updating, error;
2463 ngx_int_t rc;
2464
2465 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
2466 "http upstream not modified");
2467
2468 now = ngx_time();
2469
2470 valid = r->cache->valid_sec;
2471 updating = r->cache->updating_sec;
2472 error = r->cache->error_sec;
2473
2474 rc = u->reinit_request(r);
2475
2476 if (rc != NGX_OK) {
2477 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2478 return NGX_OK;
2479 }
2480
2481 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_REVALIDATED;
2482 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache_send(r, u);
2483
2484 if (rc == NGX_DONE) {
2485 return NGX_OK;
2486 }
2487
2488 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER) {
2489 rc = NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR;
2490 }
2491
2492 if (valid == 0) {
2493 valid = r->cache->valid_sec;
2494 updating = r->cache->updating_sec;
2495 error = r->cache->error_sec;
2496 }
2497
2498 if (valid == 0) {
2499 valid = ngx_http_file_cache_valid(u->conf->cache_valid,
2500 u->headers_in.status_n);
2501 if (valid) {
2502 valid = now + valid;
2503 }
2504 }
2505
2506 if (valid) {
2507 r->cache->valid_sec = valid;
2508 r->cache->updating_sec = updating;
2509 r->cache->error_sec = error;
2510
2511 r->cache->date = now;
2512
2513 ngx_http_file_cache_update_header(r);
2514 }
2515
2516 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2517 return NGX_OK;
2518 }
2519
2520#endif
2521
2522 return NGX_DECLINED;
2523}

2526static ngx_int_t
2527ngx_http_upstream_intercept_errors(ngx_http_request_t *r,
2528 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2529{
2530 ngx_int_t status;
2531 ngx_uint_t i;
2532 ngx_table_elt_t *h;
2533 ngx_http_err_page_t *err_page;
2534 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
2535
2536 status = u->headers_in.status_n;
2537
2538 if (status == NGX_HTTP_NOT_FOUND && u->conf->intercept_404) {
2539 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_NOT_FOUND);
2540 return NGX_OK;
2541 }
2542
2543 if (!u->conf->intercept_errors) {
2544 return NGX_DECLINED;
2545 }
2546
2547 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
2548
2549 if (clcf->error_pages == NULL) {
2550 return NGX_DECLINED;
2551 }
2552
2553 err_page = clcf->error_pages->elts;
2554 for (i = 0; i < clcf->error_pages->nelts; i++) {
2555
2556 if (err_page[i].status == status) {
2557
2558 if (status == NGX_HTTP_UNAUTHORIZED
2559 && u->headers_in.www_authenticate)
2560 {
2561 h = ngx_list_push(&r->headers_out.headers);
2562
2563 if (h == NULL) {
2564 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2565 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2566 return NGX_OK;
2567 }
2568
2569 *h = *u->headers_in.www_authenticate;
2570
2571 r->headers_out.www_authenticate = h;
2572 }
2573
2574#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2575
2576 if (r->cache) {
2577
2578 if (u->cacheable) {
2579 time_t valid;
2580
2581 valid = r->cache->valid_sec;
2582
2583 if (valid == 0) {
2584 valid = ngx_http_file_cache_valid(u->conf->cache_valid,
2585 status);
2586 if (valid) {
2587 r->cache->valid_sec = ngx_time() + valid;
2588 }
2589 }
2590
2591 if (valid) {
2592 r->cache->error = status;
2593 }
2594 }
2595
2596 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, u->pipe->temp_file);
2597 }
2598#endif
2599 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, status);
2600
2601 return NGX_OK;
2602 }
2603 }
2604
2605 return NGX_DECLINED;
2606}

2609static ngx_int_t
2610ngx_http_upstream_test_connect(ngx_connection_t *c)
2611{
2612 int err;
2613 socklen_t len;
2614
2615#if (NGX_HAVE_KQUEUE)
2616
2617 if (ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_KQUEUE_EVENT) {
2618 if (c->write->pending_eof || c->read->pending_eof) {
2619 if (c->write->pending_eof) {
2620 err = c->write->kq_errno;
2621
2622 } else {
2623 err = c->read->kq_errno;
2624 }
2625
2626 c->log->action = "connecting to upstream";
2627 (void) ngx_connection_error(c, err,
2628 "kevent() reported that connect() failed");
2629 return NGX_ERROR;
2630 }
2631
2632 } else
2633#endif
2634 {
2635 err = 0;
2636 len = sizeof(int);
2637
2638 /*
2639 * BSDs and Linux return 0 and set a pending error in err
2640 * Solaris returns -1 and sets errno
2641 */
2642
2643 if (getsockopt(c->fd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_ERROR, (void *) &err, &len)
2644 == -1)
2645 {
2646 err = ngx_socket_errno;
2647 }
2648
2649 if (err) {
2650 c->log->action = "connecting to upstream";
2651 (void) ngx_connection_error(c, err, "connect() failed");
2652 return NGX_ERROR;
2653 }
2654 }
2655
2656 return NGX_OK;
2657}

2659
2660static ngx_int_t
2661ngx_http_upstream_process_headers(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2662{
2663 ngx_str_t uri, args;
2664 ngx_uint_t i, flags;
2665 ngx_list_part_t *part;
2666 ngx_table_elt_t *h;
2667 ngx_http_upstream_header_t *hh;
2668 ngx_http_upstream_main_conf_t *umcf;
2669
2670 umcf = ngx_http_get_module_main_conf(r, ngx_http_upstream_module);
2671
2672 if (u->headers_in.x_accel_redirect
2673 && !(u->conf->ignore_headers & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_XA_REDIRECT))
2674 {
2675 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_DECLINED);
2676
2677 part = &u->headers_in.headers.part;
2678 h = part->elts;
2679
2680 for (i = 0; /* void */; i++) {
2681
2682 if (i >= part->nelts) {
2683 if (part->next == NULL) {
2684 break;
2685 }
2686
2687 part = part->next;
2688 h = part->elts;
2689 i = 0;
2690 }
2691
2692 hh = ngx_hash_find(&umcf->headers_in_hash, h[i].hash,
2693 h[i].lowcase_key, h[i].key.len);
2694
2695 if (hh && hh->redirect) {
2696 if (hh->copy_handler(r, &h[i], hh->conf) != NGX_OK) {
2697 ngx_http_finalize_request(r,
2698 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2699 return NGX_DONE;
2700 }
2701 }
2702 }
2703
2704 uri = u->headers_in.x_accel_redirect->value;
2705
2706 if (uri.data[0] == '@') {
2707 ngx_http_named_location(r, &uri);
2708
2709 } else {
2710 ngx_str_null(&args);
2711 flags = NGX_HTTP_LOG_UNSAFE;
2712
2713 if (ngx_http_parse_unsafe_uri(r, &uri, &args, &flags) != NGX_OK) {
2714 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_HTTP_NOT_FOUND);
2715 return NGX_DONE;
2716 }
2717
2718 if (r->method != NGX_HTTP_HEAD) {
2719 r->method = NGX_HTTP_GET;
2720 r->method_name = ngx_http_core_get_method;
2721 }
2722
2723 ngx_http_internal_redirect(r, &uri, &args);
2724 }
2725
2726 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_DONE);
2727 return NGX_DONE;
2728 }
2729
2730 part = &u->headers_in.headers.part;
2731 h = part->elts;
2732
2733 for (i = 0; /* void */; i++) {
2734
2735 if (i >= part->nelts) {
2736 if (part->next == NULL) {
2737 break;
2738 }
2739
2740 part = part->next;
2741 h = part->elts;
2742 i = 0;
2743 }
2744
2745 if (ngx_hash_find(&u->conf->hide_headers_hash, h[i].hash,
2746 h[i].lowcase_key, h[i].key.len))
2747 {
2748 continue;
2749 }
2750
2751 hh = ngx_hash_find(&umcf->headers_in_hash, h[i].hash,
2752 h[i].lowcase_key, h[i].key.len);
2753
2754 if (hh) {
2755 if (hh->copy_handler(r, &h[i], hh->conf) != NGX_OK) {
2756 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2757 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2758 return NGX_DONE;
2759 }
2760
2761 continue;
2762 }
2763
2764 if (ngx_http_upstream_copy_header_line(r, &h[i], 0) != NGX_OK) {
2765 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
2766 NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR);
2767 return NGX_DONE;
2768 }
2769 }
2770
2771 if (r->headers_out.server && r->headers_out.server->value.data == NULL) {
2772 r->headers_out.server->hash = 0;
2773 }
2774
2775 if (r->headers_out.date && r->headers_out.date->value.data == NULL) {
2776 r->headers_out.date->hash = 0;
2777 }
2778
2779 r->headers_out.status = u->headers_in.status_n;
2780 r->headers_out.status_line = u->headers_in.status_line;
2781
2782 r->headers_out.content_length_n = u->headers_in.content_length_n;
2783
2784 r->disable_not_modified = !u->cacheable;
2785
2786 if (u->conf->force_ranges) {
2787 r->allow_ranges = 1;
2788 r->single_range = 1;
2789
2790#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2791 if (r->cached) {
2792 r->single_range = 0;
2793 }
2794#endif
2795 }
2796
2797 u->length = -1;
2798
2799 return NGX_OK;
2800}

2802
2803static ngx_int_t
2804ngx_http_upstream_process_trailers(ngx_http_request_t *r,
2805 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2806{
2807 ngx_uint_t i;
2808 ngx_list_part_t *part;
2809 ngx_table_elt_t *h, *ho;
2810
2811 if (!u->conf->pass_trailers) {
2812 return NGX_OK;
2813 }
2814
2815 part = &u->headers_in.trailers.part;
2816 h = part->elts;
2817
2818 for (i = 0; /* void */; i++) {
2819
2820 if (i >= part->nelts) {
2821 if (part->next == NULL) {
2822 break;
2823 }
2824
2825 part = part->next;
2826 h = part->elts;
2827 i = 0;
2828 }
2829
2830 if (ngx_hash_find(&u->conf->hide_headers_hash, h[i].hash,
2831 h[i].lowcase_key, h[i].key.len))
2832 {
2833 continue;
2834 }
2835
2836 ho = ngx_list_push(&r->headers_out.trailers);
2837 if (ho == NULL) {
2838 return NGX_ERROR;
2839 }
2840
2841 *ho = h[i];
2842 }
2843
2844 return NGX_OK;
2845}

2847
2848static void
2849ngx_http_upstream_send_response(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
2850{
2851 ssize_t n;
2852 ngx_int_t rc;
2853 ngx_event_pipe_t *p;
2854 ngx_connection_t *c;
2855 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
2856
2857 rc = ngx_http_send_header(r);
2858
2859 if (rc == NGX_ERROR || rc > NGX_OK || r->post_action) {
2860 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2861 return;
2862 }
2863
2864 u->header_sent = 1;
2865
2866 if (u->upgrade) {
2867
2868#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2869
2870 if (r->cache) {
2871 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, u->pipe->temp_file);
2872 }
2873
2874#endif
2875
2876 ngx_http_upstream_upgrade(r, u);
2877 return;
2878 }
2879
2880 c = r->connection;
2881
2882 if (r->header_only) {
2883
2884 if (!u->buffering) {
2885 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2886 return;
2887 }
2888
2889 if (!u->cacheable && !u->store) {
2890 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
2891 return;
2892 }
2893
2894 u->pipe->downstream_error = 1;
2895 }
2896
2897 if (r->request_body && r->request_body->temp_file
2898 && r == r->main && !r->preserve_body)
2899 {
2900 ngx_pool_run_cleanup_file(r->pool, r->request_body->temp_file->file.fd);
2901 r->request_body->temp_file->file.fd = NGX_INVALID_FILE;
2902 }
2903
2904 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
2905
2906 if (!u->buffering) {
2907
2908#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2909
2910 if (r->cache) {
2911 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, u->pipe->temp_file);
2912 }
2913
2914#endif
2915
2916 if (u->input_filter == NULL) {
2917 u->input_filter_init = ngx_http_upstream_non_buffered_filter_init;
2918 u->input_filter = ngx_http_upstream_non_buffered_filter;
2919 u->input_filter_ctx = r;
2920 }
2921
2922 u->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_process_non_buffered_upstream;
2923 r->write_event_handler =
2924 ngx_http_upstream_process_non_buffered_downstream;
2925
2926 r->limit_rate = 0;
2927
2928 if (u->input_filter_init(u->input_filter_ctx) == NGX_ERROR) {
2929 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2930 return;
2931 }
2932
2933 if (clcf->tcp_nodelay && ngx_tcp_nodelay(c) != NGX_OK) {
2934 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2935 return;
2936 }
2937
2938 n = u->buffer.last - u->buffer.pos;
2939
2940 if (n) {
2941 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.pos;
2942
2943 u->state->response_length += n;
2944
2945 if (u->input_filter(u->input_filter_ctx, n) == NGX_ERROR) {
2946 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2947 return;
2948 }
2949
2950 ngx_http_upstream_process_non_buffered_downstream(r);
2951
2952 } else {
2953 u->buffer.pos = u->buffer.start;
2954 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.start;
2955
2956 if (ngx_http_send_special(r, NGX_HTTP_FLUSH) == NGX_ERROR) {
2957 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2958 return;
2959 }
2960
2961 if (u->peer.connection->read->ready || u->length == 0) {
2962 ngx_http_upstream_process_non_buffered_upstream(r, u);
2963 }
2964 }
2965
2966 return;
2967 }
2968
2969 /* TODO: preallocate event_pipe bufs, look "Content-Length" */
2970
2971#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
2972
2973 if (r->cache && r->cache->file.fd != NGX_INVALID_FILE) {
2974 ngx_pool_run_cleanup_file(r->pool, r->cache->file.fd);
2975 r->cache->file.fd = NGX_INVALID_FILE;
2976 }
2977
2978 switch (ngx_http_test_predicates(r, u->conf->no_cache)) {
2979
2980 case NGX_ERROR:
2981 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2982 return;
2983
2984 case NGX_DECLINED:
2985 u->cacheable = 0;
2986 break;
2987
2988 default: /* NGX_OK */
2989
2990 if (u->cache_status == NGX_HTTP_CACHE_BYPASS) {
2991
2992 /* create cache if previously bypassed */
2993
2994 if (ngx_http_file_cache_create(r) != NGX_OK) {
2995 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
2996 return;
2997 }
2998 }
2999
3000 break;
3001 }
3002
3003 if (u->cacheable) {
3004 time_t now, valid;
3005
3006 now = ngx_time();
3007
3008 valid = r->cache->valid_sec;
3009
3010 if (valid == 0) {
3011 valid = ngx_http_file_cache_valid(u->conf->cache_valid,
3012 u->headers_in.status_n);
3013 if (valid) {
3014 r->cache->valid_sec = now + valid;
3015 }
3016 }
3017
3018 if (valid) {
3019 r->cache->date = now;
3020 r->cache->body_start = (u_short) (u->buffer.pos - u->buffer.start);
3021
3022 if (u->headers_in.status_n == NGX_HTTP_OK
3023 || u->headers_in.status_n == NGX_HTTP_PARTIAL_CONTENT)
3024 {
3025 r->cache->last_modified = u->headers_in.last_modified_time;
3026
3027 if (u->headers_in.etag) {
3028 r->cache->etag = u->headers_in.etag->value;
3029
3030 } else {
3031 ngx_str_null(&r->cache->etag);
3032 }
3033
3034 } else {
3035 r->cache->last_modified = -1;
3036 ngx_str_null(&r->cache->etag);
3037 }
3038
3039 if (ngx_http_file_cache_set_header(r, u->buffer.start) != NGX_OK) {
3040 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3041 return;
3042 }
3043
3044 } else {
3045 u->cacheable = 0;
3046 }
3047 }
3048
3049 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
3050 "http cacheable: %d", u->cacheable);
3051
3052 if (u->cacheable == 0 && r->cache) {
3053 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, u->pipe->temp_file);
3054 }
3055
3056 if (r->header_only && !u->cacheable && !u->store) {
3057 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, 0);
3058 return;
3059 }
3060
3061#endif
3062
3063 p = u->pipe;
3064
3065 p->output_filter = ngx_http_upstream_output_filter;
3066 p->output_ctx = r;
3067 p->tag = u->output.tag;
3068 p->bufs = u->conf->bufs;
3069 p->busy_size = u->conf->busy_buffers_size;
3070 p->upstream = u->peer.connection;
3071 p->downstream = c;
3072 p->pool = r->pool;
3073 p->log = c->log;
3074 p->limit_rate = u->conf->limit_rate;
3075 p->start_sec = ngx_time();
3076
3077 p->cacheable = u->cacheable || u->store;
3078
3079 p->temp_file = ngx_pcalloc(r->pool, sizeof(ngx_temp_file_t));
3080 if (p->temp_file == NULL) {
3081 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3082 return;
3083 }
3084
3085 p->temp_file->file.fd = NGX_INVALID_FILE;
3086 p->temp_file->file.log = c->log;
3087 p->temp_file->path = u->conf->temp_path;
3088 p->temp_file->pool = r->pool;
3089
3090 if (p->cacheable) {
3091 p->temp_file->persistent = 1;
3092
3093#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
3094 if (r->cache && !r->cache->file_cache->use_temp_path) {
3095 p->temp_file->path = r->cache->file_cache->path;
3096 p->temp_file->file.name = r->cache->file.name;
3097 }
3098#endif
3099
3100 } else {
3101 p->temp_file->log_level = NGX_LOG_WARN;
3102 p->temp_file->warn = "an upstream response is buffered "
3103 "to a temporary file";
3104 }
3105
3106 p->max_temp_file_size = u->conf->max_temp_file_size;
3107 p->temp_file_write_size = u->conf->temp_file_write_size;
3108
3109#if (NGX_THREADS)
3110 if (clcf->aio == NGX_HTTP_AIO_THREADS && clcf->aio_write) {
3111 p->thread_handler = ngx_http_upstream_thread_handler;
3112 p->thread_ctx = r;
3113 }
3114#endif
3115
3116 p->preread_bufs = ngx_alloc_chain_link(r->pool);
3117 if (p->preread_bufs == NULL) {
3118 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3119 return;
3120 }
3121
3122 p->preread_bufs->buf = &u->buffer;
3123 p->preread_bufs->next = NULL;
3124 u->buffer.recycled = 1;
3125
3126 p->preread_size = u->buffer.last - u->buffer.pos;
3127
3128 if (u->cacheable) {
3129
3130 p->buf_to_file = ngx_calloc_buf(r->pool);
3131 if (p->buf_to_file == NULL) {
3132 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3133 return;
3134 }
3135
3136 p->buf_to_file->start = u->buffer.start;
3137 p->buf_to_file->pos = u->buffer.start;
3138 p->buf_to_file->last = u->buffer.pos;
3139 p->buf_to_file->temporary = 1;
3140 }
3141
3142 if (ngx_event_flags & NGX_USE_IOCP_EVENT) {
3143 /* the posted aio operation may corrupt a shadow buffer */
3144 p->single_buf = 1;
3145 }
3146
3147 /* TODO: p->free_bufs = 0 if use ngx_create_chain_of_bufs() */
3148 p->free_bufs = 1;
3149
3150 /*
3151 * event_pipe would do u->buffer.last += p->preread_size
3152 * as though these bytes were read
3153 */
3154 u->buffer.last = u->buffer.pos;
3155
3156 if (u->conf->cyclic_temp_file) {
3157
3158 /*
3159 * we need to disable the use of sendfile() if we use cyclic temp file
3160 * because the writing a new data may interfere with sendfile()
3161 * that uses the same kernel file pages (at least on FreeBSD)
3162 */
3163
3164 p->cyclic_temp_file = 1;
3165 c->sendfile = 0;
3166
3167 } else {
3168 p->cyclic_temp_file = 0;
3169 }
3170
3171 p->read_timeout = u->conf->read_timeout;
3172 p->send_timeout = clcf->send_timeout;
3173 p->send_lowat = clcf->send_lowat;
3174
3175 p->length = -1;
3176
3177 if (u->input_filter_init
3178 && u->input_filter_init(p->input_ctx) != NGX_OK)
3179 {
3180 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3181 return;
3182 }
3183
3184 u->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_process_upstream;
3185 r->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_process_downstream;
3186
3187 ngx_http_upstream_process_upstream(r, u);
3188}

3191static void
3192ngx_http_upstream_upgrade(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
3193{
3194 ngx_connection_t *c;
3195 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
3196
3197 c = r->connection;
3198 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
3199
3200 /* TODO: prevent upgrade if not requested or not possible */
3201
3202 if (r != r->main) {
3203 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, c->log, 0,
3204 "connection upgrade in subrequest");
3205 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3206 return;
3207 }
3208
3209 r->keepalive = 0;
3210 c->log->action = "proxying upgraded connection";
3211
3212 u->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_upgraded_read_upstream;
3213 u->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_upgraded_write_upstream;
3214 r->read_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_upgraded_read_downstream;
3215 r->write_event_handler = ngx_http_upstream_upgraded_write_downstream;
3216
3217 if (clcf->tcp_nodelay) {
3218
3219 if (ngx_tcp_nodelay(c) != NGX_OK) {
3220 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3221 return;
3222 }
3223
3224 if (ngx_tcp_nodelay(u->peer.connection) != NGX_OK) {
3225 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3226 return;
3227 }
3228 }
3229
3230 if (ngx_http_send_special(r, NGX_HTTP_FLUSH) == NGX_ERROR) {
3231 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3232 return;
3233 }
3234
3235 if (u->peer.connection->read->ready
3236 || u->buffer.pos != u->buffer.last)
3237 {
3238 ngx_post_event(c->read, &ngx_posted_events);
3239 ngx_http_upstream_process_upgraded(r, 1, 1);
3240 return;
3241 }
3242
3243 ngx_http_upstream_process_upgraded(r, 0, 1);
3244}

3276
3277static void
3278ngx_http_upstream_process_upgraded(ngx_http_request_t *r,
3279 ngx_uint_t from_upstream, ngx_uint_t do_write)
3280{
3281 size_t size;
3282 ssize_t n;
3283 ngx_buf_t *b;
3284 ngx_connection_t *c, *downstream, *upstream, *dst, *src;
3285 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
3286 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
3287
3288 c = r->connection;
3289 u = r->upstream;
3290
3291 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
3292 "http upstream process upgraded, fu:%ui", from_upstream);
3293
3294 downstream = c;
3295 upstream = u->peer.connection;
3296
3297 if (downstream->write->timedout) {
3298 c->timedout = 1;
3299 ngx_connection_error(c, NGX_ETIMEDOUT, "client timed out");
3300 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_REQUEST_TIME_OUT);
3301 return;
3302 }
3303
3304 if (upstream->read->timedout || upstream->write->timedout) {
3305 ngx_connection_error(c, NGX_ETIMEDOUT, "upstream timed out");
3306 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_GATEWAY_TIME_OUT);
3307 return;
3308 }
3309
3310 if (from_upstream) {
3311 src = upstream;
3312 dst = downstream;
3313 b = &u->buffer;
3314
3315 } else {
3316 src = downstream;
3317 dst = upstream;
3318 b = &u->from_client;
3319
3320 if (r->header_in->last > r->header_in->pos) {
3321 b = r->header_in;
3322 b->end = b->last;
3323 do_write = 1;
3324 }
3325
3326 if (b->start == NULL) {
3327 b->start = ngx_palloc(r->pool, u->conf->buffer_size);
3328 if (b->start == NULL) {
3329 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3330 return;
3331 }
3332
3333 b->pos = b->start;
3334 b->last = b->start;
3335 b->end = b->start + u->conf->buffer_size;
3336 b->temporary = 1;
3337 b->tag = u->output.tag;
3338 }
3339 }
3340
3341 for ( ;; ) {
3342
3343 if (do_write) {
3344
3345 size = b->last - b->pos;
3346
3347 if (size && dst->write->ready) {
3348
3349 n = dst->send(dst, b->pos, size);
3350
3351 if (n == NGX_ERROR) {
3352 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3353 return;
3354 }
3355
3356 if (n > 0) {
3357 b->pos += n;
3358
3359 if (b->pos == b->last) {
3360 b->pos = b->start;
3361 b->last = b->start;
3362 }
3363 }
3364 }
3365 }
3366
3367 size = b->end - b->last;
3368
3369 if (size && src->read->ready) {
3370
3371 n = src->recv(src, b->last, size);
3372
3373 if (n == NGX_AGAIN || n == 0) {
3374 break;
3375 }
3376
3377 if (n > 0) {
3378 do_write = 1;
3379 b->last += n;
3380
3381 if (from_upstream) {
3382 u->state->bytes_received += n;
3383 }
3384
3385 continue;
3386 }
3387
3388 if (n == NGX_ERROR) {
3389 src->read->eof = 1;
3390 }
3391 }
3392
3393 break;
3394 }
3395
3396 if ((upstream->read->eof && u->buffer.pos == u->buffer.last)
3397 || (downstream->read->eof && u->from_client.pos == u->from_client.last)
3398 || (downstream->read->eof && upstream->read->eof))
3399 {
3400 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, c->log, 0,
3401 "http upstream upgraded done");
3402 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, 0);
3403 return;
3404 }
3405
3406 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
3407
3408 if (ngx_handle_write_event(upstream->write, u->conf->send_lowat)
3409 != NGX_OK)
3410 {
3411 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3412 return;
3413 }
3414
3415 if (upstream->write->active && !upstream->write->ready) {
3416 ngx_add_timer(upstream->write, u->conf->send_timeout);
3417
3418 } else if (upstream->write->timer_set) {
3419 ngx_del_timer(upstream->write);
3420 }
3421
3422 if (ngx_handle_read_event(upstream->read, 0) != NGX_OK) {
3423 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3424 return;
3425 }
3426
3427 if (upstream->read->active && !upstream->read->ready) {
3428 ngx_add_timer(upstream->read, u->conf->read_timeout);
3429
3430 } else if (upstream->read->timer_set) {
3431 ngx_del_timer(upstream->read);
3432 }
3433
3434 if (ngx_handle_write_event(downstream->write, clcf->send_lowat)
3435 != NGX_OK)
3436 {
3437 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3438 return;
3439 }
3440
3441 if (ngx_handle_read_event(downstream->read, 0) != NGX_OK) {
3442 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3443 return;
3444 }
3445
3446 if (downstream->write->active && !downstream->write->ready) {
3447 ngx_add_timer(downstream->write, clcf->send_timeout);
3448
3449 } else if (downstream->write->timer_set) {
3450 ngx_del_timer(downstream->write);
3451 }
3452}

3504
3505static void
3506ngx_http_upstream_process_non_buffered_request(ngx_http_request_t *r,
3507 ngx_uint_t do_write)
3508{
3509 size_t size;
3510 ssize_t n;
3511 ngx_buf_t *b;
3512 ngx_int_t rc;
3513 ngx_connection_t *downstream, *upstream;
3514 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
3515 ngx_http_core_loc_conf_t *clcf;
3516
3517 u = r->upstream;
3518 downstream = r->connection;
3519 upstream = u->peer.connection;
3520
3521 b = &u->buffer;
3522
3523 do_write = do_write || u->length == 0;
3524
3525 for ( ;; ) {
3526
3527 if (do_write) {
3528
3529 if (u->out_bufs || u->busy_bufs || downstream->buffered) {
3530 rc = ngx_http_output_filter(r, u->out_bufs);
3531
3532 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
3533 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3534 return;
3535 }
3536
3537 ngx_chain_update_chains(r->pool, &u->free_bufs, &u->busy_bufs,
3538 &u->out_bufs, u->output.tag);
3539 }
3540
3541 if (u->busy_bufs == NULL) {
3542
3543 if (u->length == 0
3544 || (upstream->read->eof && u->length == -1))
3545 {
3546 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, 0);
3547 return;
3548 }
3549
3550 if (upstream->read->eof) {
3551 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, upstream->log, 0,
3552 "upstream prematurely closed connection");
3553
3554 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
3555 NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY);
3556 return;
3557 }
3558
3559 if (upstream->read->error) {
3560 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
3561 NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY);
3562 return;
3563 }
3564
3565 b->pos = b->start;
3566 b->last = b->start;
3567 }
3568 }
3569
3570 size = b->end - b->last;
3571
3572 if (size && upstream->read->ready) {
3573
3574 n = upstream->recv(upstream, b->last, size);
3575
3576 if (n == NGX_AGAIN) {
3577 break;
3578 }
3579
3580 if (n > 0) {
3581 u->state->bytes_received += n;
3582 u->state->response_length += n;
3583
3584 if (u->input_filter(u->input_filter_ctx, n) == NGX_ERROR) {
3585 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3586 return;
3587 }
3588 }
3589
3590 do_write = 1;
3591
3592 continue;
3593 }
3594
3595 break;
3596 }
3597
3598 clcf = ngx_http_get_module_loc_conf(r, ngx_http_core_module);
3599
3600 if (downstream->data == r) {
3601 if (ngx_handle_write_event(downstream->write, clcf->send_lowat)
3602 != NGX_OK)
3603 {
3604 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3605 return;
3606 }
3607 }
3608
3609 if (downstream->write->active && !downstream->write->ready) {
3610 ngx_add_timer(downstream->write, clcf->send_timeout);
3611
3612 } else if (downstream->write->timer_set) {
3613 ngx_del_timer(downstream->write);
3614 }
3615
3616 if (ngx_handle_read_event(upstream->read, 0) != NGX_OK) {
3617 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3618 return;
3619 }
3620
3621 if (upstream->read->active && !upstream->read->ready) {
3622 ngx_add_timer(upstream->read, u->conf->read_timeout);
3623
3624 } else if (upstream->read->timer_set) {
3625 ngx_del_timer(upstream->read);
3626 }
3627}

3636
3637static ngx_int_t
3638ngx_http_upstream_non_buffered_filter(void *data, ssize_t bytes)
3639{
3640 ngx_http_request_t *r = data;
3641
3642 ngx_buf_t *b;
3643 ngx_chain_t *cl, **ll;
3644 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
3645
3646 u = r->upstream;
3647
3648 for (cl = u->out_bufs, ll = &u->out_bufs; cl; cl = cl->next) {
3649 ll = &cl->next;
3650 }
3651
3652 cl = ngx_chain_get_free_buf(r->pool, &u->free_bufs);
3653 if (cl == NULL) {
3654 return NGX_ERROR;
3655 }
3656
3657 *ll = cl;
3658
3659 cl->buf->flush = 1;
3660 cl->buf->memory = 1;
3661
3662 b = &u->buffer;
3663
3664 cl->buf->pos = b->last;
3665 b->last += bytes;
3666 cl->buf->last = b->last;
3667 cl->buf->tag = u->output.tag;
3668
3669 if (u->length == -1) {
3670 return NGX_OK;
3671 }
3672
3673 u->length -= bytes;
3674
3675 return NGX_OK;
3676}

3877
3878static void
3879ngx_http_upstream_process_request(ngx_http_request_t *r,
3880 ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
3881{
3882 ngx_temp_file_t *tf;
3883 ngx_event_pipe_t *p;
3884
3885 p = u->pipe;
3886
3887#if (NGX_THREADS)
3888
3889 if (p->writing && !p->aio) {
3890
3891 /*
3892 * make sure to call ngx_event_pipe()
3893 * if there is an incomplete aio write
3894 */
3895
3896 if (ngx_event_pipe(p, 1) == NGX_ABORT) {
3897 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3898 return;
3899 }
3900 }
3901
3902 if (p->writing) {
3903 return;
3904 }
3905
3906#endif
3907
3908 if (u->peer.connection) {
3909
3910 if (u->store) {
3911
3912 if (p->upstream_eof || p->upstream_done) {
3913
3914 tf = p->temp_file;
3915
3916 if (u->headers_in.status_n == NGX_HTTP_OK
3917 && (p->upstream_done || p->length == -1)
3918 && (u->headers_in.content_length_n == -1
3919 || u->headers_in.content_length_n == tf->offset))
3920 {
3921 ngx_http_upstream_store(r, u);
3922 }
3923 }
3924 }
3925
3926#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
3927
3928 if (u->cacheable) {
3929
3930 if (p->upstream_done) {
3931 ngx_http_file_cache_update(r, p->temp_file);
3932
3933 } else if (p->upstream_eof) {
3934
3935 tf = p->temp_file;
3936
3937 if (p->length == -1
3938 && (u->headers_in.content_length_n == -1
3939 || u->headers_in.content_length_n
3940 == tf->offset - (off_t) r->cache->body_start))
3941 {
3942 ngx_http_file_cache_update(r, tf);
3943
3944 } else {
3945 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, tf);
3946 }
3947
3948 } else if (p->upstream_error) {
3949 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, p->temp_file);
3950 }
3951 }
3952
3953#endif
3954
3955 if (p->upstream_done || p->upstream_eof || p->upstream_error) {
3956 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
3957 "http upstream exit: %p", p->out);
3958
3959 if (p->upstream_done
3960 || (p->upstream_eof && p->length == -1))
3961 {
3962 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, 0);
3963 return;
3964 }
3965
3966 if (p->upstream_eof) {
3967 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
3968 "upstream prematurely closed connection");
3969 }
3970
3971 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY);
3972 return;
3973 }
3974 }
3975
3976 if (p->downstream_error) {
3977 ngx_log_debug0(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
3978 "http upstream downstream error");
3979
3980 if (!u->cacheable && !u->store && u->peer.connection) {
3981 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, NGX_ERROR);
3982 }
3983 }
3984}

3987static void
3988ngx_http_upstream_store(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u)
3989{
3990 size_t root;
3991 time_t lm;
3992 ngx_str_t path;
3993 ngx_temp_file_t *tf;
3994 ngx_ext_rename_file_t ext;
3995
3996 tf = u->pipe->temp_file;
3997
3998 if (tf->file.fd == NGX_INVALID_FILE) {
3999
4000 /* create file for empty 200 response */
4001
4002 tf = ngx_pcalloc(r->pool, sizeof(ngx_temp_file_t));
4003 if (tf == NULL) {
4004 return;
4005 }
4006
4007 tf->file.fd = NGX_INVALID_FILE;
4008 tf->file.log = r->connection->log;
4009 tf->path = u->conf->temp_path;
4010 tf->pool = r->pool;
4011 tf->persistent = 1;
4012
4013 if (ngx_create_temp_file(&tf->file, tf->path, tf->pool,
4014 tf->persistent, tf->clean, tf->access)
4015 != NGX_OK)
4016 {
4017 return;
4018 }
4019
4020 u->pipe->temp_file = tf;
4021 }
4022
4023 ext.access = u->conf->store_access;
4024 ext.path_access = u->conf->store_access;
4025 ext.time = -1;
4026 ext.create_path = 1;
4027 ext.delete_file = 1;
4028 ext.log = r->connection->log;
4029
4030 if (u->headers_in.last_modified) {
4031
4032 lm = ngx_parse_http_time(u->headers_in.last_modified->value.data,
4033 u->headers_in.last_modified->value.len);
4034
4035 if (lm != NGX_ERROR) {
4036 ext.time = lm;
4037 ext.fd = tf->file.fd;
4038 }
4039 }
4040
4041 if (u->conf->store_lengths == NULL) {
4042
4043 if (ngx_http_map_uri_to_path(r, &path, &root, 0) == NULL) {
4044 return;
4045 }
4046
4047 } else {
4048 if (ngx_http_script_run(r, &path, u->conf->store_lengths->elts, 0,
4049 u->conf->store_values->elts)
4050 == NULL)
4051 {
4052 return;
4053 }
4054 }
4055
4056 path.len--;
4057
4058 ngx_log_debug2(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4059 "upstream stores \"%s\" to \"%s\"",
4060 tf->file.name.data, path.data);
4061
4062 (void) ngx_ext_rename_file(&tf->file.name, &path, &ext);
4063
4064 u->store = 0;
4065}
