4075
4076static void
4077ngx_http_upstream_next(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
4078 ngx_uint_t ft_type)
4079{
4080 ngx_msec_t timeout;
4081 ngx_uint_t status, state;
4082
4083 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4084 "http next upstream, %xi", ft_type);
4085
4086 if (u->peer.sockaddr) {
4087
4088 if (ft_type == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_403
4089 || ft_type == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_404)
4090 {
4091 state = NGX_PEER_NEXT;
4092
4093 } else {
4094 state = NGX_PEER_FAILED;
4095 }
4096
4097 u->peer.free(&u->peer, u->peer.data, state);
4098 u->peer.sockaddr = NULL;
4099 }
4100
4101 if (ft_type == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_TIMEOUT) {
4102 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, NGX_ETIMEDOUT,
4103 "upstream timed out");
4104 }
4105
4106 if (u->peer.cached && ft_type == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_ERROR) {
4107 /* TODO: inform balancer instead */
4108 u->peer.tries++;
4109 }
4110
4111 switch (ft_type) {
4112
4113 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_TIMEOUT:
4114 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_504:
4115 status = NGX_HTTP_GATEWAY_TIME_OUT;
4116 break;
4117
4118 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_500:
4119 status = NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR;
4120 break;
4121
4122 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_503:
4123 status = NGX_HTTP_SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE;
4124 break;
4125
4126 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_403:
4127 status = NGX_HTTP_FORBIDDEN;
4128 break;
4129
4130 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_404:
4131 status = NGX_HTTP_NOT_FOUND;
4132 break;
4133
4134 case NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_HTTP_429:
4135 status = NGX_HTTP_TOO_MANY_REQUESTS;
4136 break;
4137
4138 /*
4139 * NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_BUSY_LOCK and NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_MAX_WAITING
4140 * never reach here
4141 */
4142
4143 default:
4144 status = NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY;
4145 }
4146
4147 if (r->connection->error) {
4148 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u,
4149 NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST);
4150 return;
4151 }
4152
4153 u->state->status = status;
4154
4155 timeout = u->conf->next_upstream_timeout;
4156
4157 if (u->request_sent
4158 && (r->method & (NGX_HTTP_POST|NGX_HTTP_LOCK|NGX_HTTP_PATCH)))
4159 {
4160 ft_type |= NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FT_NON_IDEMPOTENT;
4161 }
4162
4163 if (u->peer.tries == 0
4164 || ((u->conf->next_upstream & ft_type) != ft_type)
4165 || (u->request_sent && r->request_body_no_buffering)
4166 || (timeout && ngx_current_msec - u->peer.start_time >= timeout))
4167 {
4168#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
4169
4170 if (u->cache_status == NGX_HTTP_CACHE_EXPIRED
4171 && ((u->conf->cache_use_stale & ft_type) || r->cache->stale_error))
4172 {
4173 ngx_int_t rc;
4174
4175 rc = u->reinit_request(r);
4176
4177 if (rc != NGX_OK) {
4178 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
4179 return;
4180 }
4181
4182 u->cache_status = NGX_HTTP_CACHE_STALE;
4183 rc = ngx_http_upstream_cache_send(r, u);
4184
4185 if (rc == NGX_DONE) {
4186 return;
4187 }
4188
4189 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_INVALID_HEADER) {
4190 rc = NGX_HTTP_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR;
4191 }
4192
4193 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, rc);
4194 return;
4195 }
4196#endif
4197
4198 ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(r, u, status);
4199 return;
4200 }
4201
4202 if (u->peer.connection) {
4203 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4204 "close http upstream connection: %d",
4205 u->peer.connection->fd);
4206#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
4207
4208 if (u->peer.connection->ssl) {
4209 u->peer.connection->ssl->no_wait_shutdown = 1;
4210 u->peer.connection->ssl->no_send_shutdown = 1;
4211
4212 (void) ngx_ssl_shutdown(u->peer.connection);
4213 }
4214#endif
4215
4216 if (u->peer.connection->pool) {
4217 ngx_destroy_pool(u->peer.connection->pool);
4218 }
4219
4220 ngx_close_connection(u->peer.connection);
4221 u->peer.connection = NULL;
4222 }
4223
4224 ngx_http_upstream_connect(r, u);
4225}

4239
4240static void
4241ngx_http_upstream_finalize_request(ngx_http_request_t *r,
4242 ngx_http_upstream_t *u, ngx_int_t rc)
4243{
4244 ngx_uint_t flush;
4245
4246 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4247 "finalize http upstream request: %i", rc);
4248
4249 if (u->cleanup == NULL) {
4250 /* the request was already finalized */
4251 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_DONE);
4252 return;
4253 }
4254
4255 *u->cleanup = NULL;
4256 u->cleanup = NULL;
4257
4258 if (u->resolved && u->resolved->ctx) {
4259 ngx_resolve_name_done(u->resolved->ctx);
4260 u->resolved->ctx = NULL;
4261 }
4262
4263 if (u->state && u->state->response_time) {
4264 u->state->response_time = ngx_current_msec - u->state->response_time;
4265
4266 if (u->pipe && u->pipe->read_length) {
4267 u->state->bytes_received += u->pipe->read_length
4268 - u->pipe->preread_size;
4269 u->state->response_length = u->pipe->read_length;
4270 }
4271 }
4272
4273 u->finalize_request(r, rc);
4274
4275 if (u->peer.free && u->peer.sockaddr) {
4276 u->peer.free(&u->peer, u->peer.data, 0);
4277 u->peer.sockaddr = NULL;
4278 }
4279
4280 if (u->peer.connection) {
4281
4282#if (NGX_HTTP_SSL)
4283
4284 /* TODO: do not shutdown persistent connection */
4285
4286 if (u->peer.connection->ssl) {
4287
4288 /*
4289 * We send the "close notify" shutdown alert to the upstream only
4290 * and do not wait its "close notify" shutdown alert.
4291 * It is acceptable according to the TLS standard.
4292 */
4293
4294 u->peer.connection->ssl->no_wait_shutdown = 1;
4295
4296 (void) ngx_ssl_shutdown(u->peer.connection);
4297 }
4298#endif
4299
4300 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4301 "close http upstream connection: %d",
4302 u->peer.connection->fd);
4303
4304 if (u->peer.connection->pool) {
4305 ngx_destroy_pool(u->peer.connection->pool);
4306 }
4307
4308 ngx_close_connection(u->peer.connection);
4309 }
4310
4311 u->peer.connection = NULL;
4312
4313 if (u->pipe && u->pipe->temp_file) {
4314 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
4315 "http upstream temp fd: %d",
4316 u->pipe->temp_file->file.fd);
4317 }
4318
4319 if (u->store && u->pipe && u->pipe->temp_file
4320 && u->pipe->temp_file->file.fd != NGX_INVALID_FILE)
4321 {
4322 if (ngx_delete_file(u->pipe->temp_file->file.name.data)
4323 == NGX_FILE_ERROR)
4324 {
4325 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_CRIT, r->connection->log, ngx_errno,
4326 ngx_delete_file_n " \"%s\" failed",
4327 u->pipe->temp_file->file.name.data);
4328 }
4329 }
4330
4331#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
4332
4333 if (r->cache) {
4334
4335 if (u->cacheable) {
4336
4337 if (rc == NGX_HTTP_BAD_GATEWAY || rc == NGX_HTTP_GATEWAY_TIME_OUT) {
4338 time_t valid;
4339
4340 valid = ngx_http_file_cache_valid(u->conf->cache_valid, rc);
4341
4342 if (valid) {
4343 r->cache->valid_sec = ngx_time() + valid;
4344 r->cache->error = rc;
4345 }
4346 }
4347 }
4348
4349 ngx_http_file_cache_free(r->cache, u->pipe->temp_file);
4350 }
4351
4352#endif
4353
4354 r->read_event_handler = ngx_http_block_reading;
4355
4356 if (rc == NGX_DECLINED) {
4357 return;
4358 }
4359
4360 r->connection->log->action = "sending to client";
4361
4362 if (!u->header_sent
4363 || rc == NGX_HTTP_REQUEST_TIME_OUT
4364 || rc == NGX_HTTP_CLIENT_CLOSED_REQUEST)
4365 {
4366 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, rc);
4367 return;
4368 }
4369
4370 flush = 0;
4371
4372 if (rc >= NGX_HTTP_SPECIAL_RESPONSE) {
4373 rc = NGX_ERROR;
4374 flush = 1;
4375 }
4376
4377 if (r->header_only
4378 || (u->pipe && u->pipe->downstream_error))
4379 {
4380 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, rc);
4381 return;
4382 }
4383
4384 if (rc == 0) {
4385
4386 if (ngx_http_upstream_process_trailers(r, u) != NGX_OK) {
4387 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, NGX_ERROR);
4388 return;
4389 }
4390
4391 rc = ngx_http_send_special(r, NGX_HTTP_LAST);
4392
4393 } else if (flush) {
4394 r->keepalive = 0;
4395 rc = ngx_http_send_special(r, NGX_HTTP_FLUSH);
4396 }
4397
4398 ngx_http_finalize_request(r, rc);
4399}

4492static ngx_int_t
4493ngx_http_upstream_process_cache_control(ngx_http_request_t *r,
4494 ngx_table_elt_t *h, ngx_uint_t offset)
4495{
4496 ngx_array_t *pa;
4497 ngx_table_elt_t **ph;
4498 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
4499
4500 u = r->upstream;
4501 pa = &u->headers_in.cache_control;
4502
4503 if (pa->elts == NULL) {
4504 if (ngx_array_init(pa, r->pool, 2, sizeof(ngx_table_elt_t *)) != NGX_OK)
4505 {
4506 return NGX_ERROR;
4507 }
4508 }
4509
4510 ph = ngx_array_push(pa);
4511 if (ph == NULL) {
4512 return NGX_ERROR;
4513 }
4514
4515 *ph = h;
4516
4517#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
4518 {
4519 u_char *p, *start, *last;
4520 ngx_int_t n;
4521
4522 if (u->conf->ignore_headers & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_CACHE_CONTROL) {
4523 return NGX_OK;
4524 }
4525
4526 if (r->cache == NULL) {
4527 return NGX_OK;
4528 }
4529
4530 if (r->cache->valid_sec != 0 && u->headers_in.x_accel_expires != NULL) {
4531 return NGX_OK;
4532 }
4533
4534 start = h->value.data;
4535 last = start + h->value.len;
4536
4537 if (ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "no-cache", 8 - 1) != NULL
4538 || ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "no-store", 8 - 1) != NULL
4539 || ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "private", 7 - 1) != NULL)
4540 {
4541 u->cacheable = 0;
4542 return NGX_OK;
4543 }
4544
4545 p = ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "s-maxage=", 9 - 1);
4546 offset = 9;
4547
4548 if (p == NULL) {
4549 p = ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "max-age=", 8 - 1);
4550 offset = 8;
4551 }
4552
4553 if (p) {
4554 n = 0;
4555
4556 for (p += offset; p < last; p++) {
4557 if (*p == ',' || *p == ';' || *p == ' ') {
4558 break;
4559 }
4560
4561 if (*p >= '0' && *p <= '9') {
4562 n = n * 10 + (*p - '0');
4563 continue;
4564 }
4565
4566 u->cacheable = 0;
4567 return NGX_OK;
4568 }
4569
4570 if (n == 0) {
4571 u->cacheable = 0;
4572 return NGX_OK;
4573 }
4574
4575 r->cache->valid_sec = ngx_time() + n;
4576 }
4577
4578 p = ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "stale-while-revalidate=",
4579 23 - 1);
4580
4581 if (p) {
4582 n = 0;
4583
4584 for (p += 23; p < last; p++) {
4585 if (*p == ',' || *p == ';' || *p == ' ') {
4586 break;
4587 }
4588
4589 if (*p >= '0' && *p <= '9') {
4590 n = n * 10 + (*p - '0');
4591 continue;
4592 }
4593
4594 u->cacheable = 0;
4595 return NGX_OK;
4596 }
4597
4598 r->cache->updating_sec = n;
4599 r->cache->error_sec = n;
4600 }
4601
4602 p = ngx_strlcasestrn(start, last, (u_char *) "stale-if-error=", 15 - 1);
4603
4604 if (p) {
4605 n = 0;
4606
4607 for (p += 15; p < last; p++) {
4608 if (*p == ',' || *p == ';' || *p == ' ') {
4609 break;
4610 }
4611
4612 if (*p >= '0' && *p <= '9') {
4613 n = n * 10 + (*p - '0');
4614 continue;
4615 }
4616
4617 u->cacheable = 0;
4618 return NGX_OK;
4619 }
4620
4621 r->cache->error_sec = n;
4622 }
4623 }
4624#endif
4625
4626 return NGX_OK;
4627}

4670static ngx_int_t
4671ngx_http_upstream_process_accel_expires(ngx_http_request_t *r,
4672 ngx_table_elt_t *h, ngx_uint_t offset)
4673{
4674 ngx_http_upstream_t *u;
4675
4676 u = r->upstream;
4677 u->headers_in.x_accel_expires = h;
4678
4679#if (NGX_HTTP_CACHE)
4680 {
4681 u_char *p;
4682 size_t len;
4683 ngx_int_t n;
4684
4685 if (u->conf->ignore_headers & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_XA_EXPIRES) {
4686 return NGX_OK;
4687 }
4688
4689 if (r->cache == NULL) {
4690 return NGX_OK;
4691 }
4692
4693 len = h->value.len;
4694 p = h->value.data;
4695
4696 if (p[0] != '@') {
4697 n = ngx_atoi(p, len);
4698
4699 switch (n) {
4700 case 0:
4701 u->cacheable = 0;
4702 /* fall through */
4703
4704 case NGX_ERROR:
4705 return NGX_OK;
4706
4707 default:
4708 r->cache->valid_sec = ngx_time() + n;
4709 return NGX_OK;
4710 }
4711 }
4712
4713 p++;
4714 len--;
4715
4716 n = ngx_atoi(p, len);
4717
4718 if (n != NGX_ERROR) {
4719 r->cache->valid_sec = n;
4720 }
4721 }
4722#endif
4723
4724 return NGX_OK;
4725}

4755{

4760

4838static ngx_int_t
4839ngx_http_upstream_process_vary(ngx_http_request_t *r,

4848
4849 if (u->conf->ignore_headers & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_IGN_VARY) {
4850 return NGX_OK;
4851 }
4852
4853 if (r->cache == NULL) {
4854 return NGX_OK;
4855 }
4856
4857 if (h->value.len > NGX_HTTP_CACHE_VARY_LEN
4858 || (h->value.len == 1 && h->value.data[0] == '*'))
4859 {
4860 u->cacheable = 0;
4861 }
4862
4863 r->cache->vary = h->value;
4864
4865#endif
4866
4867 return NGX_OK;
4868}

4927static ngx_int_t
4928ngx_http_upstream_copy_content_type(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_table_elt_t *h,
4929 ngx_uint_t offset)
4930{
4931 u_char *p, *last;
4932
4933 r->headers_out.content_type_len = h->value.len;
4934 r->headers_out.content_type = h->value;
4935 r->headers_out.content_type_lowcase = NULL;
4936
4937 for (p = h->value.data; *p; p++) {
4938
4939 if (*p != ';') {
4940 continue;
4941 }
4942
4943 last = p;
4944
4945 while (*++p == ' ') { /* void */ }
4946
4947 if (*p == '\0') {
4948 return NGX_OK;
4949 }
4950
4951 if (ngx_strncasecmp(p, (u_char *) "charset=", 8) != 0) {
4952 continue;
4953 }
4954
4955 p += 8;
4956
4957 r->headers_out.content_type_len = last - h->value.data;
4958
4959 if (*p == '"') {
4960 p++;
4961 }
4962
4963 last = h->value.data + h->value.len;
4964
4965 if (*(last - 1) == '"') {
4966 last--;
4967 }
4968
4969 r->headers_out.charset.len = last - p;
4970 r->headers_out.charset.data = p;
4971
4972 return NGX_OK;
4973 }
4974
4975 return NGX_OK;
4976}

5000static ngx_int_t
5001ngx_http_upstream_rewrite_location(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_table_elt_t *h,
5002 ngx_uint_t offset)
5003{
5004 ngx_int_t rc;
5005 ngx_table_elt_t *ho;
5006
5007 ho = ngx_list_push(&r->headers_out.headers);
5008 if (ho == NULL) {
5009 return NGX_ERROR;
5010 }
5011
5012 *ho = *h;
5013
5014 if (r->upstream->rewrite_redirect) {
5015 rc = r->upstream->rewrite_redirect(r, ho, 0);
5016
5017 if (rc == NGX_DECLINED) {
5018 return NGX_OK;
5019 }
5020
5021 if (rc == NGX_OK) {
5022 r->headers_out.location = ho;
5023
5024 ngx_log_debug1(NGX_LOG_DEBUG_HTTP, r->connection->log, 0,
5025 "rewritten location: \"%V\"", &ho->value);
5026 }
5027
5028 return rc;
5029 }
5030
5031 if (ho->value.data[0] != '/') {
5032 r->headers_out.location = ho;
5033 }
5034
5035 /*
5036 * we do not set r->headers_out.location here to avoid handling
5037 * relative redirects in ngx_http_header_filter()
5038 */
5039
5040 return NGX_OK;
5041}

5205static ngx_int_t
5206ngx_http_upstream_addr_variable(ngx_http_request_t *r,
5207 ngx_http_variable_value_t *v, uintptr_t data)
5208{
5209 u_char *p;
5210 size_t len;
5211 ngx_uint_t i;
5212 ngx_http_upstream_state_t *state;
5213
5214 v->valid = 1;
5215 v->no_cacheable = 0;
5216 v->not_found = 0;
5217
5218 if (r->upstream_states == NULL || r->upstream_states->nelts == 0) {
5219 v->not_found = 1;
5220 return NGX_OK;
5221 }
5222
5223 len = 0;
5224 state = r->upstream_states->elts;
5225
5226 for (i = 0; i < r->upstream_states->nelts; i++) {
5227 if (state[i].peer) {
5228 len += state[i].peer->len + 2;
5229
5230 } else {
5231 len += 3;
5232 }
5233 }
5234
5235 p = ngx_pnalloc(r->pool, len);
5236 if (p == NULL) {
5237 return NGX_ERROR;
5238 }
5239
5240 v->data = p;
5241
5242 i = 0;
5243
5244 for ( ;; ) {
5245 if (state[i].peer) {
5246 p = ngx_cpymem(p, state[i].peer->data, state[i].peer->len);
5247 }
5248
5249 if (++i == r->upstream_states->nelts) {
5250 break;
5251 }
5252
5253 if (state[i].peer) {
5254 *p++ = ',';
5255 *p++ = ' ';
5256
5257 } else {
5258 *p++ = ' ';
5259 *p++ = ':';
5260 *p++ = ' ';
5261
5262 if (++i == r->upstream_states->nelts) {
5263 break;
5264 }
5265
5266 continue;
5267 }
5268 }
5269
5270 v->len = p - v->data;
5271
5272 return NGX_OK;
5273}

5341static ngx_int_t
5342ngx_http_upstream_response_time_variable(ngx_http_request_t *r,
5343 ngx_http_variable_value_t *v, uintptr_t data)
5344{
5345 u_char *p;
5346 size_t len;
5347 ngx_uint_t i;
5348 ngx_msec_int_t ms;
5349 ngx_http_upstream_state_t *state;
5350
5351 v->valid = 1;
5352 v->no_cacheable = 0;
5353 v->not_found = 0;
5354
5355 if (r->upstream_states == NULL || r->upstream_states->nelts == 0) {
5356 v->not_found = 1;
5357 return NGX_OK;
5358 }
5359
5360 len = r->upstream_states->nelts * (NGX_TIME_T_LEN + 4 + 2);
5361
5362 p = ngx_pnalloc(r->pool, len);
5363 if (p == NULL) {
5364 return NGX_ERROR;
5365 }
5366
5367 v->data = p;
5368
5369 i = 0;
5370 state = r->upstream_states->elts;
5371
5372 for ( ;; ) {
5373 if (state[i].status) {
5374
5375 if (data == 1 && state[i].header_time != (ngx_msec_t) -1) {
5376 ms = state[i].header_time;
5377
5378 } else if (data == 2 && state[i].connect_time != (ngx_msec_t) -1) {
5379 ms = state[i].connect_time;
5380
5381 } else {
5382 ms = state[i].response_time;
5383 }
5384
5385 ms = ngx_max(ms, 0);
5386 p = ngx_sprintf(p, "%T.%03M", (time_t) ms / 1000, ms % 1000);
5387
5388 } else {
5389 *p++ = '-';
5390 }
5391
5392 if (++i == r->upstream_states->nelts) {
5393 break;
5394 }
5395
5396 if (state[i].peer) {
5397 *p++ = ',';
5398 *p++ = ' ';
5399
5400 } else {
5401 *p++ = ' ';
5402 *p++ = ':';
5403 *p++ = ' ';
5404
5405 if (++i == r->upstream_states->nelts) {
5406 break;
5407 }
5408
5409 continue;
5410 }
5411 }
5412
5413 v->len = p - v->data;
5414
5415 return NGX_OK;
5416}

5637 ngx_conf_t pcf;
5638 ngx_http_module_t *module;
5639 ngx_http_conf_ctx_t *ctx, *http_ctx;
5640 ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t *uscf;
5641
5642 ngx_memzero(&u, sizeof(ngx_url_t));
5643
5644 value = cf->args->elts;
5645 u.host = value[1];
5646 u.no_resolve = 1;
5647 u.no_port = 1;
5648
5649 uscf = ngx_http_upstream_add(cf, &u, NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE
5650 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_WEIGHT
5651 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_MAX_CONNS
5652 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_MAX_FAILS
5653 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FAIL_TIMEOUT
5654 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_DOWN
5655 |NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_BACKUP);
5656 if (uscf == NULL) {
5657 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5658 }
5659
5660
5661 ctx = ngx_pcalloc(cf->pool, sizeof(ngx_http_conf_ctx_t));
5662 if (ctx == NULL) {
5663 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5664 }
5665
5666 http_ctx = cf->ctx;
5667 ctx->main_conf = http_ctx->main_conf;
5668
5669 /* the upstream{}'s srv_conf */
5670
5671 ctx->srv_conf = ngx_pcalloc(cf->pool, sizeof(void *) * ngx_http_max_module);
5672 if (ctx->srv_conf == NULL) {
5673 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5674 }
5675
5676 ctx->srv_conf[ngx_http_upstream_module.ctx_index] = uscf;
5677
5678 uscf->srv_conf = ctx->srv_conf;
5679
5680
5681 /* the upstream{}'s loc_conf */
5682
5683 ctx->loc_conf = ngx_pcalloc(cf->pool, sizeof(void *) * ngx_http_max_module);
5684 if (ctx->loc_conf == NULL) {
5685 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5686 }
5687
5688 for (m = 0; cf->cycle->modules[m]; m++) {
5689 if (cf->cycle->modules[m]->type != NGX_HTTP_MODULE) {
5690 continue;
5691 }
5692
5693 module = cf->cycle->modules[m]->ctx;
5694
5695 if (module->create_srv_conf) {
5696 mconf = module->create_srv_conf(cf);
5697 if (mconf == NULL) {
5698 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5699 }
5700
5701 ctx->srv_conf[cf->cycle->modules[m]->ctx_index] = mconf;
5702 }
5703
5704 if (module->create_loc_conf) {
5705 mconf = module->create_loc_conf(cf);
5706 if (mconf == NULL) {
5707 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5708 }
5709
5710 ctx->loc_conf[cf->cycle->modules[m]->ctx_index] = mconf;
5711 }
5712 }
5713
5714 uscf->servers = ngx_array_create(cf->pool, 4,
5715 sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_server_t));
5716 if (uscf->servers == NULL) {
5717 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5718 }
5719
5720
5721 /* parse inside upstream{} */
5722
5723 pcf = *cf;
5724 cf->ctx = ctx;
5725 cf->cmd_type = NGX_HTTP_UPS_CONF;
5726
5727 rv = ngx_conf_parse(cf, NULL);
5728
5729 *cf = pcf;
5730
5731 if (rv != NGX_CONF_OK) {
5732 return rv;
5733 }
5734
5735 if (uscf->servers->nelts == 0) {
5736 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5737 "no servers are inside upstream");
5738 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5739 }
5740
5741 return rv;
5742}

5744
5745static char *
5746ngx_http_upstream_server(ngx_conf_t *cf, ngx_command_t *cmd, void *conf)
5747{
5748 ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t *uscf = conf;
5749
5750 time_t fail_timeout;
5751 ngx_str_t *value, s;
5752 ngx_url_t u;
5753 ngx_int_t weight, max_conns, max_fails;
5754 ngx_uint_t i;
5755 ngx_http_upstream_server_t *us;
5756
5757 us = ngx_array_push(uscf->servers);
5758 if (us == NULL) {
5759 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5760 }
5761
5762 ngx_memzero(us, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_server_t));
5763
5764 value = cf->args->elts;
5765
5766 weight = 1;
5767 max_conns = 0;
5768 max_fails = 1;
5769 fail_timeout = 10;
5770
5771 for (i = 2; i < cf->args->nelts; i++) {
5772
5773 if (ngx_strncmp(value[i].data, "weight=", 7) == 0) {
5774
5775 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_WEIGHT)) {
5776 goto not_supported;
5777 }
5778
5779 weight = ngx_atoi(&value[i].data[7], value[i].len - 7);
5780
5781 if (weight == NGX_ERROR || weight == 0) {
5782 goto invalid;
5783 }
5784
5785 continue;
5786 }
5787
5788 if (ngx_strncmp(value[i].data, "max_conns=", 10) == 0) {
5789
5790 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_MAX_CONNS)) {
5791 goto not_supported;
5792 }
5793
5794 max_conns = ngx_atoi(&value[i].data[10], value[i].len - 10);
5795
5796 if (max_conns == NGX_ERROR) {
5797 goto invalid;
5798 }
5799
5800 continue;
5801 }
5802
5803 if (ngx_strncmp(value[i].data, "max_fails=", 10) == 0) {
5804
5805 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_MAX_FAILS)) {
5806 goto not_supported;
5807 }
5808
5809 max_fails = ngx_atoi(&value[i].data[10], value[i].len - 10);
5810
5811 if (max_fails == NGX_ERROR) {
5812 goto invalid;
5813 }
5814
5815 continue;
5816 }
5817
5818 if (ngx_strncmp(value[i].data, "fail_timeout=", 13) == 0) {
5819
5820 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_FAIL_TIMEOUT)) {
5821 goto not_supported;
5822 }
5823
5824 s.len = value[i].len - 13;
5825 s.data = &value[i].data[13];
5826
5827 fail_timeout = ngx_parse_time(&s, 1);
5828
5829 if (fail_timeout == (time_t) NGX_ERROR) {
5830 goto invalid;
5831 }
5832
5833 continue;
5834 }
5835
5836 if (ngx_strcmp(value[i].data, "backup") == 0) {
5837
5838 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_BACKUP)) {
5839 goto not_supported;
5840 }
5841
5842 us->backup = 1;
5843
5844 continue;
5845 }
5846
5847 if (ngx_strcmp(value[i].data, "down") == 0) {
5848
5849 if (!(uscf->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_DOWN)) {
5850 goto not_supported;
5851 }
5852
5853 us->down = 1;
5854
5855 continue;
5856 }
5857
5858 goto invalid;
5859 }
5860
5861 ngx_memzero(&u, sizeof(ngx_url_t));
5862
5863 u.url = value[1];
5864 u.default_port = 80;
5865
5866 if (ngx_parse_url(cf->pool, &u) != NGX_OK) {
5867 if (u.err) {
5868 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5869 "%s in upstream \"%V\"", u.err, &u.url);
5870 }
5871
5872 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5873 }
5874
5875 us->name = u.url;
5876 us->addrs = u.addrs;
5877 us->naddrs = u.naddrs;
5878 us->weight = weight;
5879 us->max_conns = max_conns;
5880 us->max_fails = max_fails;
5881 us->fail_timeout = fail_timeout;
5882
5883 return NGX_CONF_OK;
5884
5885invalid:
5886
5887 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5888 "invalid parameter \"%V\"", &value[i]);
5889
5890 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5891
5892not_supported:
5893
5894 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5895 "balancing method does not support parameter \"%V\"",
5896 &value[i]);
5897
5898 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
5899}

5901
5902ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t *
5903ngx_http_upstream_add(ngx_conf_t *cf, ngx_url_t *u, ngx_uint_t flags)
5904{
5905 ngx_uint_t i;
5906 ngx_http_upstream_server_t *us;
5907 ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t *uscf, **uscfp;
5908 ngx_http_upstream_main_conf_t *umcf;
5909
5910 if (!(flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE)) {
5911
5912 if (ngx_parse_url(cf->pool, u) != NGX_OK) {
5913 if (u->err) {
5914 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5915 "%s in upstream \"%V\"", u->err, &u->url);
5916 }
5917
5918 return NULL;
5919 }
5920 }
5921
5922 umcf = ngx_http_conf_get_module_main_conf(cf, ngx_http_upstream_module);
5923
5924 uscfp = umcf->upstreams.elts;
5925
5926 for (i = 0; i < umcf->upstreams.nelts; i++) {
5927
5928 if (uscfp[i]->host.len != u->host.len
5929 || ngx_strncasecmp(uscfp[i]->host.data, u->host.data, u->host.len)
5930 != 0)
5931 {
5932 continue;
5933 }
5934
5935 if ((flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE)
5936 && (uscfp[i]->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE))
5937 {
5938 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5939 "duplicate upstream \"%V\"", &u->host);
5940 return NULL;
5941 }
5942
5943 if ((uscfp[i]->flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE) && !u->no_port) {
5944 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
5945 "upstream \"%V\" may not have port %d",
5946 &u->host, u->port);
5947 return NULL;
5948 }
5949
5950 if ((flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE) && !uscfp[i]->no_port) {
5951 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf->log, 0,
5952 "upstream \"%V\" may not have port %d in %s:%ui",
5953 &u->host, uscfp[i]->port,
5954 uscfp[i]->file_name, uscfp[i]->line);
5955 return NULL;
5956 }
5957
5958 if (uscfp[i]->port && u->port
5959 && uscfp[i]->port != u->port)
5960 {
5961 continue;
5962 }
5963
5964 if (flags & NGX_HTTP_UPSTREAM_CREATE) {
5965 uscfp[i]->flags = flags;
5966 uscfp[i]->port = 0;
5967 }
5968
5969 return uscfp[i];
5970 }
5971
5972 uscf = ngx_pcalloc(cf->pool, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_srv_conf_t));
5973 if (uscf == NULL) {
5974 return NULL;
5975 }
5976
5977 uscf->flags = flags;
5978 uscf->host = u->host;
5979 uscf->file_name = cf->conf_file->file.name.data;
5980 uscf->line = cf->conf_file->line;
5981 uscf->port = u->port;
5982 uscf->no_port = u->no_port;
5983
5984 if (u->naddrs == 1 && (u->port || u->family == AF_UNIX)) {
5985 uscf->servers = ngx_array_create(cf->pool, 1,
5986 sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_server_t));
5987 if (uscf->servers == NULL) {
5988 return NULL;
5989 }
5990
5991 us = ngx_array_push(uscf->servers);
5992 if (us == NULL) {
5993 return NULL;
5994 }
5995
5996 ngx_memzero(us, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_server_t));
5997
5998 us->addrs = u->addrs;
5999 us->naddrs = 1;
6000 }
6001
6002 uscfp = ngx_array_push(&umcf->upstreams);
6003 if (uscfp == NULL) {
6004 return NULL;
6005 }
6006
6007 *uscfp = uscf;
6008
6009 return uscf;
6010}

6012
6013char *
6014ngx_http_upstream_bind_set_slot(ngx_conf_t *cf, ngx_command_t *cmd,
6015 void *conf)
6016{
6017 char *p = conf;
6018
6019 ngx_int_t rc;
6020 ngx_str_t *value;
6021 ngx_http_complex_value_t cv;
6022 ngx_http_upstream_local_t **plocal, *local;
6023 ngx_http_compile_complex_value_t ccv;
6024
6025 plocal = (ngx_http_upstream_local_t **) (p + cmd->offset);
6026
6027 if (*plocal != NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR) {
6028 return "is duplicate";
6029 }
6030
6031 value = cf->args->elts;
6032
6033 if (cf->args->nelts == 2 && ngx_strcmp(value[1].data, "off") == 0) {
6034 *plocal = NULL;
6035 return NGX_CONF_OK;
6036 }
6037
6038 ngx_memzero(&ccv, sizeof(ngx_http_compile_complex_value_t));
6039
6040 ccv.cf = cf;
6041 ccv.value = &value[1];
6042 ccv.complex_value = &cv;
6043
6044 if (ngx_http_compile_complex_value(&ccv) != NGX_OK) {
6045 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6046 }
6047
6048 local = ngx_pcalloc(cf->pool, sizeof(ngx_http_upstream_local_t));
6049 if (local == NULL) {
6050 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6051 }
6052
6053 *plocal = local;
6054
6055 if (cv.lengths) {
6056 local->value = ngx_palloc(cf->pool, sizeof(ngx_http_complex_value_t));
6057 if (local->value == NULL) {
6058 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6059 }
6060
6061 *local->value = cv;
6062
6063 } else {
6064 local->addr = ngx_palloc(cf->pool, sizeof(ngx_addr_t));
6065 if (local->addr == NULL) {
6066 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6067 }
6068
6069 rc = ngx_parse_addr_port(cf->pool, local->addr, value[1].data,
6070 value[1].len);
6071
6072 switch (rc) {
6073 case NGX_OK:
6074 local->addr->name = value[1];
6075 break;
6076
6077 case NGX_DECLINED:
6078 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
6079 "invalid address \"%V\"", &value[1]);
6080 /* fall through */
6081
6082 default:
6083 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6084 }
6085 }
6086
6087 if (cf->args->nelts > 2) {
6088 if (ngx_strcmp(value[2].data, "transparent") == 0) {
6089#if (NGX_HAVE_TRANSPARENT_PROXY)
6090 ngx_core_conf_t *ccf;
6091
6092 ccf = (ngx_core_conf_t *) ngx_get_conf(cf->cycle->conf_ctx,
6093 ngx_core_module);
6094
6095 ccf->transparent = 1;
6096 local->transparent = 1;
6097#else
6098 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
6099 "transparent proxying is not supported "
6100 "on this platform, ignored");
6101#endif
6102 } else {
6103 ngx_conf_log_error(NGX_LOG_EMERG, cf, 0,
6104 "invalid parameter \"%V\"", &value[2]);
6105 return NGX_CONF_ERROR;
6106 }
6107 }
6108
6109 return NGX_CONF_OK;
6110}

6113static ngx_int_t
6114ngx_http_upstream_set_local(ngx_http_request_t *r, ngx_http_upstream_t *u,
6115 ngx_http_upstream_local_t *local)
6116{
6117 ngx_int_t rc;
6118 ngx_str_t val;
6119 ngx_addr_t *addr;
6120
6121 if (local == NULL) {
6122 u->peer.local = NULL;
6123 return NGX_OK;
6124 }
6125
6126#if (NGX_HAVE_TRANSPARENT_PROXY)
6127 u->peer.transparent = local->transparent;
6128#endif
6129
6130 if (local->value == NULL) {
6131 u->peer.local = local->addr;
6132 return NGX_OK;
6133 }
6134
6135 if (ngx_http_complex_value(r, local->value, &val) != NGX_OK) {
6136 return NGX_ERROR;
6137 }
6138
6139 if (val.len == 0) {
6140 return NGX_OK;
6141 }
6142
6143 addr = ngx_palloc(r->pool, sizeof(ngx_addr_t));
6144 if (addr == NULL) {
6145 return NGX_ERROR;
6146 }
6147
6148 rc = ngx_parse_addr_port(r->pool, addr, val.data, val.len);
6149 if (rc == NGX_ERROR) {
6150 return NGX_ERROR;
6151 }
6152
6153 if (rc != NGX_OK) {
6154 ngx_log_error(NGX_LOG_ERR, r->connection->log, 0,
6155 "invalid local address \"%V\"", &val);
6156 return NGX_OK;
6157 }
6158
6159 addr->name = val;
6160 u->peer.local = addr;
6161
6162 return NGX_OK;
6163}

6209
6210ngx_int_t
6211ngx_http_upstream_hide_headers_hash(ngx_conf_t *cf,
6212 ngx_http_upstream_conf_t *conf, ngx_http_upstream_conf_t *prev,
6213 ngx_str_t *default_hide_headers, ngx_hash_init_t *hash)
6214{
6215 ngx_str_t *h;
6216 ngx_uint_t i, j;
6217 ngx_array_t hide_headers;
6218 ngx_hash_key_t *hk;
6219
6220 if (conf->hide_headers == NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR
6221 && conf->pass_headers == NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR)
6222 {
6223 conf->hide_headers = prev->hide_headers;
6224 conf->pass_headers = prev->pass_headers;
6225
6226 conf->hide_headers_hash = prev->hide_headers_hash;
6227
6228 if (conf->hide_headers_hash.buckets) {
6229 return NGX_OK;
6230 }
6231
6232 } else {
6233 if (conf->hide_headers == NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR) {
6234 conf->hide_headers = prev->hide_headers;
6235 }
6236
6237 if (conf->pass_headers == NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR) {
6238 conf->pass_headers = prev->pass_headers;
6239 }
6240 }
6241
6242 if (ngx_array_init(&hide_headers, cf->temp_pool, 4, sizeof(ngx_hash_key_t))
6243 != NGX_OK)
6244 {
6245 return NGX_ERROR;
6246 }
6247
6248 for (h = default_hide_headers; h->len; h++) {
6249 hk = ngx_array_push(&hide_headers);
6250 if (hk == NULL) {
6251 return NGX_ERROR;
6252 }
6253
6254 hk->key = *h;
6255 hk->key_hash = ngx_hash_key_lc(h->data, h->len);
6256 hk->value = (void *) 1;
6257 }
6258
6259 if (conf->hide_headers != NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR) {
6260
6261 h = conf->hide_headers->elts;
6262
6263 for (i = 0; i < conf->hide_headers->nelts; i++) {
6264
6265 hk = hide_headers.elts;
6266
6267 for (j = 0; j < hide_headers.nelts; j++) {
6268 if (ngx_strcasecmp(h[i].data, hk[j].key.data) == 0) {
6269 goto exist;
6270 }
6271 }
6272
6273 hk = ngx_array_push(&hide_headers);
6274 if (hk == NULL) {
6275 return NGX_ERROR;
6276 }
6277
6278 hk->key = h[i];
6279 hk->key_hash = ngx_hash_key_lc(h[i].data, h[i].len);
6280 hk->value = (void *) 1;
6281
6282 exist:
6283
6284 continue;
6285 }
6286 }
6287
6288 if (conf->pass_headers != NGX_CONF_UNSET_PTR) {
6289
6290 h = conf->pass_headers->elts;
6291 hk = hide_headers.elts;
6292
6293 for (i = 0; i < conf->pass_headers->nelts; i++) {
6294 for (j = 0; j < hide_headers.nelts; j++) {
6295
6296 if (hk[j].key.data == NULL) {
6297 continue;
6298 }
6299
6300 if (ngx_strcasecmp(h[i].data, hk[j].key.data) == 0) {
6301 hk[j].key.data = NULL;
6302 break;
6303 }
6304 }
6305 }
6306 }
6307
6308 hash->hash = &conf->hide_headers_hash;
6309 hash->key = ngx_hash_key_lc;
6310 hash->pool = cf->pool;
6311 hash->temp_pool = NULL;
6312
6313 if (ngx_hash_init(hash, hide_headers.elts, hide_headers.nelts) != NGX_OK) {
6314 return NGX_ERROR;
6315 }
6316
6317 /*
6318 * special handling to preserve conf->hide_headers_hash
6319 * in the "http" section to inherit it to all servers
6320 */
6321
6322 if (prev->hide_headers_hash.buckets == NULL
6323 && conf->hide_headers == prev->hide_headers
6324 && conf->pass_headers == prev->pass_headers)
6325 {
6326 prev->hide_headers_hash = conf->hide_headers_hash;
6327 }
6328
6329 return NGX_OK;
6330}
